{"type":"message","id":"b895dd09","parentId":"ee4f8d74","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:26:44.853Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying they've authorized on the Feishu website, but we're still having issues. Let me try a different approach - maybe I can use the feishu_im_user_search_messages or feishu_im_user_get_thread_messages to find the message where they mentioned me in the group.\n\nActually, let me first try to get the group messages again. Maybe the issue is that the web authorization hasn't propagated to the API permissions yet.\n\nWait - the user said they authorized on the Feishu website. This might mean they went to open.feishu.cn and authorized the app there, not through the in-app authorization card I sent. That kind of authorization might be different from the OAuth flow we're using.\n \nLet me search for messages where the user mentioned the bot in that group to see what's actually there.","thinkingSignature":"03bfdc76707a95b8b849afd0c8086f5efb5063e052a3ac9cab97e88712c466a2"},{"type":"text","text":"明白，你在飞书网站授权了，但API可能存在刷新延迟。让我换个方式直接搜索群里你@我的那条消息。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i29tbw7yl41k_1","name":"feishu_im_user_search_messages","arguments":{"query":"@","chat_id":"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22","relative_time":"this_week"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":270,"cacheRead":42013,"cacheWrite":852,"totalTokens":43268,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776043596469,"responseId":"062b794c40c5f9591e5caae97feff338"}}
