{"type":"message","id":"a382afd2","parentId":"de6f21cc","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:27:02.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It says 1 permission needed. Let me wait for the user to authorize again.\n\nActually, I wonder if the issue is that the user authorization and the app-level authorization are different things. In Feishu, there are:\n1. App-level permissions (set by the app developer in the console)\n2. User-level permissions (when a user grants access to their data)\n\nThe `search:message` scope might be an app-level permission that needs to be configured in the Feishu Open Platform console, not something the user can authorize through our OAuth flow.\n\nLet me inform the user about this distinction and suggest they check if the app has been approved with the proper permissions in the Feishu Open Platform.","thinkingSignature":"27ed7e0234e896a09f48777c3c54ae80f45d25e36c66bf45291ed214dbe3fb9c"},{"type":"text","text":"还差1个权限（`search:message`），已发送授权卡片。\n\n不过我怀疑这个问题可能不只是授权能解决的——`search:message` 可能是**应用级别**的权限，需要在飞书开放平台的应用配置中开通，不一定是我们这个授权流程能解决的。\n\n你方便的话可以去这里看看：\n1. 登录 [飞书开放平台](https://open.feishu.cn/app) → 找到 `coding-agent` 应用\n2. 查看 **权限管理** → 搜索 `im:message.group_msg:get_as_user` 和 `search:message`\n3. 确认这些权限是否已经申请并生效\n\n如果应用缺少这些权限，需要在开放平台申请权限并发布新版本，授权卡片是解决不了的。\n\n你先授权当前这个，然后我们看看能不能调通。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8316,"output":313,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43835,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776043611790,"responseId":"062b795bbb8c42815c93811949caf255"}}
