{"type":"message","id":"b9eb5574","parentId":"3cf26700","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:27:40.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still failing. It seems the `search:message` permission requires application-level authorization in the Feishu Open Platform, not user-level authorization. The user authorization flow isn't covering this permission.\n\nLet me explain this to the user - the `search:message` scope needs to be enabled at the application level in the Feishu Open Platform. User authorization can only grant user-level scopes, but some scopes like `search:message` may require the application to have been configured with those scopes from the start.\n\nLet me be direct with the user about this limitation.","thinkingSignature":"d28169e5f9a55dfbc8a5f9431b4cc443c1f2f955431244a3211232b057a722b9"},{"type":"text","text":"授权卡片流程对 `search:message` 这个权限不起作用——它是**应用级别**的权限，需要在飞书开放平台的应用配置中开通，光用户授权解决不了。\n\n**解决方案：**\n\n1. 你需要去飞书开放平台手动给 `coding-agent` 应用添加这个权限：\n   - 登录 https://open.feishu.cn/app\n   - 找到你的应用 → **权限管理**\n   - 搜索 `im:message.group_msg:get_as_user` 和 `search:message`，申请并开通\n   - 创建新版本并发布\n\n2. 或者，我可以换个方式——用**我已经有的权限**（`im:chat:read`）先获取群里最近的消息，找找你@我的那条内容，虽然没有搜索权限，但正常读取应该是可以的。\n\n要不我先试试直接获取群消息看看能不能读到？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":8725,"output":289,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44220,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776043651202,"responseId":"062b7983a78b454b67a8a1e0e0bc2b98"}}
