{"type":"message","id":"e521a99b","parentId":"4e1991fb","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:31:23.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the news-market skill to understand how it works.","thinkingSignature":"c48daf6cf5bbfe70160aa1f678fb2ee917e04dc7b37d8b31dda8602d07800092"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l5abqy336g30_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/news-market/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":27819,"output":49,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63074,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776043880602,"responseId":"062b7a68d783a3fd2991c33a4ab17a19"}}
{"type":"message","id":"dba1c4d5","parentId":"e521a99b","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:31:23.332Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l5abqy336g30_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: news-market\ndescription: 全球股市早间要闻生成技能。用于每天早上生成包含全球股市相关新闻、大盘体温、板块映射、看涨/看跌判断的早间报告。触发场景：(1) 每天08:50定时执行 (2) 用户手动触发\"生成早间要闻\"或\"今日股市消息\"\n---\n\n# News Market - 全球股市早间要闻\n\n## Overview\n\n生成每日全球股市早间要闻报告，包含：\n- 全球股市相关新闻摘要\n- A股大盘体温（涨跌停、成交量、情绪指标）\n- 板块涨跌热力图\n- 看涨/看跌判断及操作建议\n\n## 使用方式\n\n### 手动触发\n用户发送以下指令时执行：\n- \"生成早间要闻\"\n- \"今日股市消息\"\n- \"全球股市早餐\"\n\n### 定时任务\n每天 08:50 自动执行（需配置 cron）\n\n## 数据来源\n\n1. **A股数据**：AkShare / 腾讯财经\n2. **港股数据**：AkShare\n3. **美股数据**：yfinance\n4. **新闻资讯**：东方财富网、同花顺\n\n## 输出格式\n\n生成结构化报告，包含：\n1. 📈 **全球市场概览** - 各主要市场涨跌幅\n2. 🇨🇳 **A股大盘体温** - 涨跌停数量、成交量、情绪评分\n3. 🔥 **板块热力图** - 涨幅前5/跌幅前5\n4. 🎯 **判断与建议** - 看涨/看跌、仓位建议\n\n## 脚本执行\n\n```bash\n# 生成早间报告\npython3 scripts/generate_morning_news.py\n\n# 指定输出路径\npython3 scripts/generate_morning_news.py --output /path/to/report.md\n```\n\n## 配置项 (scripts/config.py)\n\n- `REPORT_TIME`: 报告生成时间\n- `MARKETS`: 关注的市场列表\n- `SECTOR_COUNT`: 板块显示数量\n- `FEISHU_WEBHOOK`: 飞书推送地址（可选）\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776043883324}}
{"type":"message","id":"39a8cba5","parentId":"dba1c4d5","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:31:34.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the news-market skill, it says news comes from eastsmoney (东方财富网) and THS (同花顺). But the specific item \"小米股票为何跌跌不休\" is from TrendRadar based on the user's message. \n\nThe TrendRadar data appears to aggregate from multiple sources. The original news item about 小米股票 likely came from one of the news portals that TrendRadar monitors.\n\nLet me try to search for this news using a different search engine, or let me try using the firecrawl skill or browser to find the source.\n\nActually, let me try using the firecrawl skill to search for the news. But first, let me see if there's a way to find the source from the TrendRadar output. The issue is the web_source_fusion_daily_latest.json is stale (from April 1), but the morning news was generated today (April 13) based on data from TrendRadar.\n\nActually, looking at the group message, the news was included in the 财经热点早报 sent at 08:01 today. The source listed was \"TrendRadar\" - it seems like TrendRadar aggregates news from various sources and the original source of \"小米股票为何跌跌不休\" may not have been explicitly listed in the summary.\n\nLet me try to do a web search to find this specific article. Let me try a different approach - use the firecrawl or try the multi-search-engine skill.","thinkingSignature":"0bdb0e4a0696a737adf0ce6babb8c5936786201833dffde72419a5780114cb87"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gmpvqj7d00yh_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":28318,"output":339,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63863,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776043883333,"responseId":"062b7a6b9f709eb2f72fa16e18b9fa8c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"59e8c22a","parentId":"39a8cba5","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:31:34.200Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gmpvqj7d00yh_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: \"Multi search engine integration with 17 engines (8 CN + 9 Global). Supports advanced search operators, time filters, site search, privacy engines, and WolframAlpha knowledge queries. No API keys required.\"\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `site:` | `site:github.com python` | Search within site |\n| `filetype:` | `filetype:pdf report` | Specific file type |\n| `\"\"` | `\"machine learning\"` | Exact match |\n| `-` | `python -snake` | Exclude term |\n| `OR` | `cat OR dog` | Either term |\n\n## Time Filters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `tbs=qdr:h` | Past hour |\n| `tbs=qdr:d` | Past day |\n| `tbs=qdr:w` | Past week |\n| `tbs=qdr:m` | Past month |\n| `tbs=qdr:y` | Past year |\n\n## Privacy Engines\n\n- **DuckDuckGo**: No tracking\n- **Startpage**: Google results + privacy\n- **Brave**: Independent index\n- **Qwant**: EU GDPR compliant\n\n## Bangs Shortcuts (DuckDuckGo)\n\n| Bang | Destination |\n|------|-------------|\n| `!g` | Google |\n| `!gh` | GitHub |\n| `!so` | Stack Overflow |\n| `!w` | Wikipedia |\n| `!yt` | YouTube |\n\n## WolframAlpha Queries\n\n- Math: `integrate x^2 dx`\n- Conversion: `100 USD to CNY`\n- Stocks: `AAPL stock`\n- Weather: `weather in Beijing`\n\n## Documentation\n\n- `references/advanced-search.md` - Domestic search guide\n- `references/international-search.md` - International search guide\n- `CHANGELOG.md` - Version history\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776043894191}}
