{"type":"message","id":"afe4d847","parentId":"6dcdbe71","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:33:02.993Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3y5jm6r0k201_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# Skill Evolver — 每日定时回顾\n# 每天 21:00 执行\n\nDATE_STR=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nSKILL_DIR=\"$(cd \"$(dirname \"$0\")\" && cd .. && pwd)\"\nLOG_FILE=\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/memory/skill_evolution_log.md\"\n\necho \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] 开始 Skill Evolver 每日回顾\" >> \"$SKILL_DIR/logs/daily_review.log\" 2>&1\n\ncd \"$SKILL_DIR\" || exit 1\n\nRESULT=$(node scripts/skill_evolver.js --mode=review --date=\"$DATE_STR\" 2>&1)\necho \"$RESULT\" >> \"$SKILL_DIR/logs/daily_review.log\" 2>&1\n\necho \"$RESULT\"\n\n# 如果有候选机会，记录并输出摘要供 cron 推送\nif echo \"$RESULT\" | grep -q \"候选\"; then\n  echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] 回顾完成，有候选沉淀机会\" >> \"$SKILL_DIR/logs/daily_review.log\"\nelse\n  echo \"[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')] 回顾完成，无新增沉淀机会\" >> \"$SKILL_DIR/logs/daily_review.log\"\nfi\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776043982984}}
{"type":"message","id":"ef6ebc02","parentId":"afe4d847","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:33:07.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This doesn't look like the skill update check report. The message showed a table with skill names, status, and reasons. Let me look for the clawhub skill which handles skill updates.","thinkingSignature":"fa872b179cfc0ab13457cf1afc15ceaa2d9882fd10b51c98adf07baadaa552c6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pvs7tbulmy64_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/Library/pnpm/global/5/.pnpm/openclaw@2026.4.10_@emnapi+core@1.9.2_@emnapi+runtime@1.9.2_@napi-rs+canvas@0.1.97_@typ_a90ffd2929abe8f398b8e8e6d84b8ef0/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35577,"output":156,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70939,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776043982993,"responseId":"062b7acf294080d3e1918db47c6e9391"}}
{"type":"message","id":"870ad0ca","parentId":"ef6ebc02","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:33:07.472Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pvs7tbulmy64_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776043987463}}
{"type":"message","id":"525d201b","parentId":"870ad0ca","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:33:14.614Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is the ClawHub CLI skill. The skill update report was generated by a script that uses `clawhub list` or similar. Let me search for where this daily update check is happening. Looking at the message again:\n\n```\n以下是该每日更新检查报告：\n———\n**① clawhub skills 更新检查**\n\n```PLAIN_TEXT\n| Skill                | 状态   | 原因                                                            |\n| -------------------- | ---- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |\n| multi-search-engine  | ⏭ 跳过 | 本地有改动（local changes）                                          |\n```\n\nThis was from a system message generated by something that checks clawhub skills daily. It could be a cron task or a script in the workspace. Let me search for it.","thinkingSignature":"d5e3c4e18ad8ab805d4ff1f760ea037f456479f985aec780874eb9e204c9e845"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ip42lhubppix_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/ 2>/dev/null | grep -i \"skill\\|update\\|check\" | head -10","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36167,"output":220,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71593,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776043987472,"responseId":"062b7ad3d5e288debdb2d543dc043d96"}}
