{"type":"message","id":"2639c0af","parentId":"e00bb672","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:37:13.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The script works. I see some issues though:\n\n1. The VirusTotal check is catching things like `api_key` in SKILL.md descriptions (which are normal), so we need to be more specific about what constitutes a real risk\n2. The \"⏭ 跳过\" for skills that don't exist in SKILL_DIR (like `todo-tracker`) is confusing - these might be skills that were uninstalled but still in the clawhub list\n\nBut overall the structure works. Let me improve the script to:\n1. Fix the VirusTotal check to only flag actual code files, not documentation\n2. Handle skills that exist in clawhub list but not in SKILL_DIR\n3. Add more nuance to the recommendations\n\n\n4. Now I'm going to refine the script with these improvements.","thinkingSignature":"1091c0afa9ff82f112a2b744fbcf582a0216d171f88f7acd584187c85292f561"},{"type":"text","text":"脚本能跑了，但有几个问题需要修正：\n\n1. VirusTotal 检查太宽泛，把 SKILL.md 里的 `api_key` 也误判了\n2. `todo-tracker` 等不在本地目录的 skill 显示\"跳过\"不够清晰\n3. `xiaohongshu-skill` 被标记为高风险，但实际是 Skill.md 里描述性文字包含敏感词\n\n我来修正这些问题：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a8tohgr43s6r_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSkill Update Checker — 改进版 v2\n对比本地 skill 与远程版本，提供明确的升级建议\n\n改进点：\n1. 本地有改动时，分析 diff 内容而非直接跳过\n2. 高风险模式只检查实际代码文件（.py/.js/.sh），不检查文档\n3. 区分\"未安装\"vs\"本地有定制\"vs\"可以更新\"\n4. 给出明确建议：保留 / 更新 / 需要review\n\"\"\"\n\nimport subprocess\nimport json\nimport os\nimport hashlib\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Optional\n\nHOME = Path.home()\nSKILL_DIR = HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"skills\"\nWORKSPACE = HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\n\n# 高风险模式（仅检查代码文件）\nHIGH_RISK_PATTERNS = [\n    \"eval(\", \"exec(\", \"subprocess(\", \"os.system(\",\n    \"crypto\", \"hashlib\", \"hmac\",\n    \"requests.\", \"urllib\", \"http.request\",\n    \"shell=True\",\n]\n\n# 敏感信息模式（检查配置文件和代码）\nSENSITIVE_PATTERNS = [\n    \"api_key\", \"secret\", \"password\", \"token\",\n    \"private_key\", \"access_token\",\n]\n\n\ndef run_cmd(cmd: str, cwd: Optional[str] = None) -> tuple[str, int]:\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            cmd, shell=True, capture_output=True, text=True,\n            cwd=cwd, timeout=60\n        )\n        return result.stdout.strip(), result.returncode\n    except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n        return \"\", -1\n    except Exception as e:\n        return str(e), -1\n\n\ndef get_installed_skills() -> list[dict]:\n    stdout, rc = run_cmd(\"clawhub list\")\n    if rc != 0 or not stdout:\n        return []\n    skills = []\n    for line in stdout.strip().split(\"\\n\"):\n        parts = line.strip().split()\n        if len(parts) >= 2:\n            skills.append({\"name\": parts[0], \"version\": parts[1]})\n    return skills\n\n\ndef get_local_skill_info(skill_name: str) -> dict:\n    skill_path = SKILL_DIR / skill_name\n    if not skill_path.exists():\n        return {\"exists\": False}\n\n    # 读取 SKILL.md 的 description\n    skill_md = skill_path / \"SKILL.md\"\n    description = \"\"\n    if skill_md.exists():\n        content = skill_md.read_text(errors=\"ignore\")\n        for line in content.split(\"\\n\"):\n            if line.strip().startswith(\"description:\"):\n                description = line.split(\"description:\", 1)[1].strip().strip('\"|')\n                break\n\n    # 检查是否有 git\n    has_git = (skill_path / \".git\").exists()\n\n    # 文件列表（排除 .git 等）\n    code_files = []\n    all_files = []\n    for f in skill_path.rglob(\"*\"):\n        if f.is_file():\n            rel = str(f.relative_to(skill_path))\n            if any(p in rel for p in [\".git\", \"node_modules\", \"__pycache__\", \".DS_Store\"]):\n                continue\n            all_files.append(rel)\n            if f.suffix in [\".py\", \".js\", \".sh\"]:\n                code_files.append(rel)\n\n    return {\n        \"exists\": True,\n        \"path\": str(skill_path),\n        \"description\": description,\n        \"has_git\": has_git,\n        \"all_file_count\": len(all_files),\n        \"code_file_count\": len(code_files),\n        \"code_files\": code_files,\n    }\n\n\ndef check_code_risks(skill_name: str, skill_path: Path) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"只检查代码文件中的高风险模式\"\"\"\n    findings = []\n    for f in skill_path.rglob(\"*\"):\n        if f.is_file() and f.suffix in [\".py\", \".js\", \".sh\"]:\n            try:\n                content = f.read_text(errors=\"ignore\")\n                rel = str(f.relative_to(skill_path))\n                for pattern in HIGH_RISK_PATTERNS:\n                    if pattern in content:\n                        findings.append(f\"{rel}: '{pattern}'\")\n            except:\n                pass\n    return {\n        \"flagged\": len(findings) > 0,\n        \"count\": len(findings),\n        \"samples\": findings[:3],\n    }\n\n\ndef get_remote_version(skill_name: str) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"尝试获取远程版本\"\"\"\n    # clawhub search 返回 slug+版本信息\n    stdout, rc = run_cmd(f\"clawhub search {skill_name} 2>/dev/null\")\n    if rc == 0 and stdout:\n        # 查找匹配行\n        for line in stdout.strip().split(\"\\n\"):\n            if line.strip().startswith(skill_name):\n                parts = line.strip().split()\n                if len(parts) >= 2:\n                    return {\"available\": True, \"remote_version\": parts[1]}\n    return {\"available\": False}\n\n\ndef compute_recommendation(skill_name: str, local: dict, remote: dict, risk: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"计算最终建议\"\"\"\n    \n    # case 1: skill 本地不存在（已卸载但 clawhub 还记录）\n    if not local[\"exists\"]:\n        return {\n            \"status\": \"not_installed\",\n            \"risk\": \"-\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⏭ 未安装\",\n            \"reason\": \"本地目录不存在，可能已卸载\"\n        }\n\n    # case 2: 有高风险代码模式\n    if risk[\"flagged\"]:\n        return {\n            \"status\": \"needs_review\",\n            \"risk\": \"HIGH\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⚠️ 需review\",\n            \"reason\": f\"代码中发现{len(risk['samples'])}处高风险模式: {', '.join(risk['samples'][:2])}\"\n        }\n\n    # case 3: 无 git + 代码文件多 → 可能有重要定制\n    if not local[\"has_git\"] and local[\"code_file_count\"] > 3:\n        return {\n            \"status\": \"review_recommended\",\n            \"risk\": \"MEDIUM\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"🔍 建议保留\",\n            \"reason\": f\"无版本控制，有{local['code_file_count']}个代码文件，可能有重要定制\"\n        }\n\n    # case 4: 有 git → 可以比对 diff\n    if local[\"has_git\"]:\n        stdout, _ = run_cmd(f\"cd {local['path']} && git status --porcelain 2>/dev/null\")\n        has_changes = bool(stdout.strip())\n        if has_changes:\n            # 获取 diff 统计\n            diff_stat, _ = run_cmd(f\"cd {local['path']} && git diff --stat 2>/dev/null\")\n            return {\n                \"status\": \"has_local_changes\",\n                \"risk\": \"LOW\",\n                \"recommendation\": \"✅ 保留本地\",\n                \"reason\": f\"有本地改动（git追踪）: {diff_stat.strip()[:100]}\" if diff_stat else \"有本地改动（git追踪）\"\n            }\n        else:\n            return {\n                \"status\": \"clean\",\n                \"risk\": \"LOW\",\n                \"recommendation\": \"🔄 可更新\",\n                \"reason\": \"本地无改动，与远程同步\"\n            }\n\n    # case 5: 无 git 但代码文件少 → 可能是轻度定制\n    return {\n        \"status\": \"possibly_modified\",\n        \"risk\": \"LOW\",\n        \"recommendation\": \"✅ 保留本地\",\n        \"reason\": f\"无版本控制但改动较少（{local['code_file_count']}个代码文件），保留本地版本\"\n    }\n\n\ndef check_skill(skill_name: str) -> dict:\n    local = get_local_skill_info(skill_name)\n    remote = get_remote_version(skill_name)\n    \n    if local[\"exists\"]:\n        skill_path = SKILL_DIR / skill_name\n        risk = check_code_risks(skill_name, skill_path)\n    else:\n        risk = {\"flagged\": False, \"count\": 0, \"samples\": []}\n    \n    rec = compute_recommendation(skill_name, local, remote, risk)\n\n    return {\n        \"name\": skill_name,\n        \"version\": local.get(\"version\", remote.get(\"remote_version\", \"?\")),\n        \"installed\": local[\"exists\"],\n        \"has_git\": local.get(\"has_git\", False),\n        \"code_files\": local.get(\"code_file_count\", 0),\n        \"remote_version\": remote.get(\"remote_version\"),\n        \"status\": rec[\"status\"],\n        \"risk\": rec[\"risk\"],\n        \"recommendation\": rec[\"recommendation\"],\n        \"reason\": rec[\"reason\"],\n    }\n\n\ndef main():\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    print(\"🔍 Skill Update Checker v2.1 — 改进版\")\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    \n    skills = get_installed_skills()\n    if not skills:\n        print(\"\\n❌ 未找到已安装的 skills\")\n        return\n    \n    print(f\"\\n📦 共发现 {len(skills)} 个已安装 skills\\n\")\n    \n    results = [check_skill(s[\"name\"]) for s in skills]\n    \n    # 分组显示\n    print(\"┌\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┐\")\n    print(f\"│ {'Skill':<26} {'风险':^5} {'状态':^22} │\")\n    print(\"├\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┤\")\n    \n    for r in results:\n        rec = r.get(\"recommendation\", \"⏭ 跳过\")\n        risk = r.get(\"risk\", \"-\")\n        status = r.get(\"status\", \"-\")[:20]\n        name = r[\"name\"][:25]\n        print(f\"│ {name:<26} {risk:^5} {rec[:20]:^22} │\")\n    \n    print(\"└\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┘\")\n    \n    # 详细分析\n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 62)\n    print(\"📋 详细分析\")\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    \n    categories = {\n        \"⚠️ 需review\": [r for r in results if r[\"risk\"] == \"HIGH\"],\n        \"🔍 建议保留\": [r for r in results if r[\"risk\"] == \"MEDIUM\"],\n        \"✅ 保留本地\": [r for r in results if r[\"risk\"] == \"LOW\" and r[\"status\"] in (\"has_local_changes\", \"possibly_modified\", \"not_installed\")],\n        \"🔄 可更新\": [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] == \"clean\"],\n    }\n    \n    for cat, items in categories.items():\n        if not items:\n            continue\n        print(f\"\\n{cat}（{len(items)} 个）：\")\n        for r in items:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n            print(f\"    {r['reason']}\")\n    \n    # 汇总\n    actionable = len(categories[\"⚠️ 需review\"]) + len(categories[\"🔍 建议保留\"])\n    updateable = len(categories[\"🔄 可更新\"])\n    print(f\"\\n📊 汇总：{actionable} 个需关注，{updateable} 个可更新\")\n    \n    # 保存 JSON\n    output_path = WORKSPACE / \"memory\" / \"skill_update_check.json\"\n    output_path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    with open(output_path, \"w\") as f:\n        json.dump(results, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    print(f\"📄 报告已保存: {output_path}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":48228,"output":2797,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86231,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776044181125,"responseId":"062b7b956ef1bd30c03fb9dc4c9d6791"}}
