{"type":"message","id":"f39ad874","parentId":"7cc0bd3a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:38:49.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the script runs quickly and gives meaningful results. I see that:\n\n1. Most skills listed by `clawhub list` don't actually exist in `~/.openclaw/skills/` - they're either uninstalled or installed elsewhere (like `~/.openclaw/skills/` contains more than what's in clawhub list)\n2. The 17 \"未安装\" ones are in clawhub's list but not in the local skills directory\n3. `xiaohongshu-skill` is flagged as needing review because it has 11 code files and no git\n4. `multi-search-engine` and `context-memory-optimizer` are flagged as \"轻量定制\"\n\n\n5. The `clawhub list` output doesn't accurately reflect what's actually installed locally, so I need to reconcile these discrepancies.","thinkingSignature":"0a6efa2c89551ea7d7f001a704f536bc962cfdf37e604a8131d6adcff88f3140"},{"type":"text","text":"脚本跑通了！但我注意到一个重要问题：`clawhub list` 显示 20 个 skills，但实际本地只有 3 个存在于 `~/.openclaw/skills/` 目录下。其余 17 个显示\"未安装\"——说明它们要么已卸载，要么装到了别的地方。\n\n这意味着原报告里那些\"本地有改动\"的 skill（multi-search-engine 等），实际上可能根本不在本地目录里，可能是从别的地方装过来的。\n\n**你能告诉我：**\n\n1. 你的 skills 是装在 `~/.openclaw/skills/` 还是其他地方？\n2. 原来的每日更新检查报告是从哪里触发的？是 cron 任务还是手动脚本？\n\n这样我才能找到原始脚本在哪，以及确认 skill 实际的存放位置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54061,"output":312,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89579,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776044318717,"responseId":"062b7c1e8aeed826c2c747aba3be1101"}}
