{"type":"message","id":"31c11a05","parentId":"2c546d42","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:41:40.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The skills are in `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/`, not `~/.openclaw/skills/`. That's why the original script couldn't find them - it was looking in the wrong directory. Now let me update the `skill_update_check.py` to point to the correct directory. Also, I should update the script so that when it finds skills, it actually checks them against the correct path. Let me also quickly look at the original skill update report to understand where it was getting its info from.\n\nThe user mentioned that the skills update check report comes from somewhere. Let me search for the original script.","thinkingSignature":"0403dc1676abdc369c854a58665729a9e3ef78d33105d124b4f34e29c20522bd"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！Skills 实际装在 **`~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/`**，不是 `~/.openclaw/skills/`。原脚本找错目录了。\n\n这就是问题所在——原报告用的路径不对，所以一直报\"本地有改动\"但找不到文件。我来修正检查脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g9ydtac4kt83_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSkill Update Checker v4 — 正确路径版本\nSkills 实际路径: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n\"\"\"\n\nimport subprocess\nimport json\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nHOME = Path.home())\nSKILL_DIR = HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\" / \"skills\"   # 正确路径\nWORKSPACE = HOME / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\n\n\ndef run_cmd(cmd: str, timeout: int = 10) -> tuple[str, int]:\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(cmd, shell=True, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=timeout)\n        return result.stdout.strip(), result.returncode\n    except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n        return \"\", -1\n    except Exception as e:\n        return str(e), -1\n\n\ndef get_installed_skills() -> list[dict]:\n    \"\"\"从 clawhub list 获取已安装 skills\"\"\"\n    stdout, rc = run_cmd(\"clawhub list\")\n    if rc != 0 or not stdout:\n        return []\n    return [{\"name\": p[0], \"version\": p[1]} for p in [l.strip().split() for l in stdout.strip().split(\"\\n\")] if len(p) >= 2]\n\n\ndef check_skill(skill_name: str) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"检查单个 skill\"\"\"\n    skill_path = SKILL_DIR / skill_name\n    exists = skill_path.exists()\n    \n    if not exists:\n        return {\n            \"name\": skill_name,\n            \"status\": \"not_installed\",\n            \"risk\": \"-\",\n            \"recommendation\": \"⏭ 未安装\",\n            \"reason\": \"本地不存在\",\n            \"installed\": False,\n        }\n    \n    # 检查 .git\n    has_git = (skill_path / \".git\").exists()\n    \n    # 统计代码文件\n    code_files = []\n    all_files = []\n    try:\n        for f in skill_path.rglob(\"*\"):\n            if f.is_file() and \".git\" not in str(f) and \"node_modules\" not in str(f):\n                rel = str(f.relative_to(skill_path))\n                all_files.append(rel)\n                if f.suffix in [\".py\", \".js\", \".sh\"]:\n                    code_files.append(rel)\n    except:\n        pass\n    \n    code_count = len(code_files)\n    \n    # 高风险代码检查（只查代码文件）\n    risk_samples = []\n    try:\n        for f in skill_path.rglob(\"*\"):\n            if f.is_file() and f.suffix in [\".py\", \".js\", \".sh\"]:\n                if \".git\" in str(f) or \"node_modules\" in str(f):\n                    continue\n                try:\n                    content = f.read_text(errors=\"ignore\", size=8000)\n                    for pattern in [\"eval(\", \"exec(\", \"subprocess(\", \"os.system(\", \"requests.\", \"shell=True\"]:\n                        if pattern in content:\n                            rel = str(f.relative_to(skill_path))\n                            risk_samples.append(f\"{rel}:{pattern}\")\n                except:\n                    pass\n    except:\n        pass\n    \n    # 判断状态\n    if risk_samples:\n        status = \"needs_review\"\n        risk = \"HIGH\"\n        recommendation = \"⚠️ 需review\"\n        reason = f\"代码含: {risk_samples[0]}\"\n    elif not has_git and code_count > 3:\n        status = \"likely_modified\"\n        risk = \"MEDIUM\"\n        recommendation = \"🔍 建议保留\"\n        reason = f\"无git，有{code_count}个代码文件，可能有定制\"\n    elif has_git:\n        # 检查是否有未提交改动（git status --porcelain）\n        status_out, _ = run_cmd(f\"cd {skill_path} && git status --porcelain 2>/dev/null\", timeout=5)\n        has_changes = bool(status_out.strip())\n        if has_changes:\n            diff_stat, _ = run_cmd(f\"cd {skill_path} && git diff --stat 2>/dev/null\", timeout=5)\n            status = \"has_local_changes\"\n            risk = \"LOW\"\n            recommendation = \"✅ 保留本地\"\n            reason = f\"有本地改动: {diff_stat.strip()[:80]}\" if diff_stat else \"有本地改动\"\n        else:\n            status = \"clean\"\n            risk = \"LOW\"\n            recommendation = \"🔄 可更新\"\n            reason = \"与远程无差异\"\n    else:\n        status = \"light_modification\"\n        risk = \"LOW\"\n        recommendation = \"✅ 保留本地\"\n        reason = f\"轻量定制（{code_count}个代码文件）\"\n    \n    return {\n        \"name\": skill_name,\n        \"status\": status,\n        \"risk\": risk,\n        \"recommendation\": recommendation,\n        \"reason\": reason,\n        \"installed\": True,\n        \"has_git\": has_git,\n        \"code_count\": code_count,\n        \"file_count\": len(all_files),\n    }\n\n\ndef main():\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    print(\"🔍 Skill Update Checker v4 — 正确路径\")\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    print(f\"\\n📂 Skills 目录: {SKILL_DIR}\")\n    \n    skills = get_installed_skills()\n    print(f\"📦 clawhub 记录: {len(skills)} 个\\n\")\n    \n    results = []\n    for s in skills:\n        r = check_skill(s[\"name\"])\n        r[\"version\"] = s[\"version\"]\n        results.append(r)\n    \n    # 分列显示\n    print(\"┌\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┐\")\n    print(f\"│ {'Skill':<26} {'风险':^5} {'建议':^22} │\")\n    print(\"├\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┤\")\n    for r in results:\n        rec = r.get(\"recommendation\", \"⏭ 跳过\")\n        risk = r.get(\"risk\", \"-\")\n        name = r[\"name\"][:25]\n        print(f\"│ {name:<26} {risk:^5} {rec[:20]:^22} │\")\n    print(\"└\" + \"─\" * 60 + \"┘\")\n    \n    # 分类汇总\n    high = [r for r in results if r[\"risk\"] == \"HIGH\"]\n    med = [r for r in results if r[\"risk\"] == \"MEDIUM\"]\n    clean = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] == \"clean\"]\n    changes = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] == \"has_local_changes\"]\n    light = [r for r in results if r[\"status\"] in (\"light_modification\", \"likely_modified\")]\n    not_inst = [r for r in results if not r[\"installed\"]]\n    \n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 62)\n    print(\"📋 详细分析\")\n    print(\"=\" * 62)\n    \n    if high:\n        print(f\"\\n⚠️  需review（{len(high)} 个）：\")\n        for r in high:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r['reason']}\")\n    \n    if med:\n        print(f\"\\n🔍 建议保留（{len(med)} 个）：\")\n        for r in med:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}: {r['reason']}\")\n    \n    if clean:\n        print(f\"\\n🔄 可更新（{len(clean)} 个）：\")\n        for r in clean:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n    \n    if changes:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 保留本地（{len(changes)} 个，有git改动）：\")\n        for r in changes:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n            print(f\"    {r['reason']}\")\n    \n    if light:\n        print(f\"\\n✅ 保留本地（{len(light)} 个，轻量定制）：\")\n        for r in light:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n    \n    if not_inst:\n        print(f\"\\n⏭  未安装（{len(not_inst)} 个）：\")\n        for r in not_inst:\n            print(f\"  • {r['name']}\")\n    \n    print(f\"\\n📊 汇总：⚠️{len(high)} 🔍{len(med)} 🔄{len(clean)} ✅{len(changes)+len(light)} ⏭{len(not_inst)}\")\n    \n    # 保存\n    out = WORKSPACE / \"memory\" / \"skill_update_check.json\"\n    out.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    with open(out, \"w\") as f:\n        json.dump(results, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    print(f\"\\n📄 已保存: {out}\")\n\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57099,"output":2112,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94417,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776044465105,"responseId":"062b7cb1786d4ad3a89505d45a2239a7"}}
