{"type":"message","id":"8785ebb5","parentId":"f677265a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:43:23.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The port is closed or timing out. But the user said their computer hasn't blocked THS ports. So the issue is likely that the TDX server IPs have changed or the service is no longer available.\n\nLet me try to check if there's a more current list of TDX server IPs, or if there's an alternative way to get market data.","thinkingSignature":"5feaa650468a5c037f605f1923a0c849e0b66090f157dd37a00147846ca9a079"},{"type":"text","text":"端口测试：直接用 `nc` 检测 `101.227.73.36:7709` → **关闭/超时**。\n\n但你说的对，这不是你 Mac mini 防火墙的问题——是**目标服务器的端口不再响应**。同花顺的服务器 IP 可能已经变更或服务下线了。\n\n让我搜一下当前可用的 TDX 服务器地址：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3wk8ax3taira_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\n# 尝试从 github 上找最新的 pytdx 服务器列表\nimport urllib.request\ntry:\n    url = 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/\\\\Pe板凳/pytdx/master/pytdx/config.py'\n    resp = urllib.request.urlopen(url, timeout=5)\n    content = resp.read().decode('utf-8')\n    # 找 IP 相关内容\n    for line in content.split('\\n'):\n        if 'HQ' in line or '7709' in line or 'ip' in line.lower():\n            print(line)\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print('获取失败:', e)\n\" 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61854,"output":311,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776044593747,"responseId":"062b7d32d4164ad3031c2380631b5ce9"}}
