{"type":"message","id":"3300055d","parentId":"c083cf92","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:43:53.207Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found a useful result - cnblogs article about getting pytdx server IPs. Let me scrape that page.","thinkingSignature":"a7d218657435e72d611466f24fefb1038f0d4a9df1a85b6577261b2b4f22af9d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9ugbmt5tnoid_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent && firecrawl scrape \"https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/18456471\" --only-main-content -o .firecrawl/pytdx_ip.md 2>&1 && cat .firecrawl/pytdx_ip.md | head -100","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":63181,"output":133,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98520,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776044628834,"responseId":"062b7d553b0dbbf00afae6e59718cd23"}}
{"type":"message","id":"68f719b6","parentId":"3300055d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:44:01.180Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9ugbmt5tnoid_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"随笔\\- 184\n文章\\- 1\n评论\\- 28\n阅读\\-\n\n59万\n\n[![订阅](https://www.cnblogs.com/skins/uandme/images/xml.gif)](https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/rss/)\n\n# [获取pytdx行情服务器ip和port](https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/18456471 \"发布于 2024-10-10 15:32\")\n\n之前一直用的api.connect('124.71.187.122', 7709)突然不能用了，调查了一下，给出如下解决方案\n\n打开通达信客户端，选项->通讯设置。\n\n![](https://img2024.cnblogs.com/blog/154823/202410/154823-20241010152843606-524113945.png)\n\n![](https://img2024.cnblogs.com/blog/154823/202410/154823-20241010152929222-379405919.png)\n\n勾掉\"登录时查找最快的主站\"，手动选择\"行情主站\"，点确定。\n\n点击\"选项\"中的\"断开行情主站\"，再点\"连接行情主站\"。\n\n打开windows任务管理器，找到通达信进程的PID，比如58596。\n\n打开cmd，输入netstat -ano \\| findstr \"58596\"\n\n![](https://img2024.cnblogs.com/blog/154823/202410/154823-20241010153035779-2105625771.png)\n\n端口号7709的IP，即为所选通达信行情主站的IP地址。\n\n免责声明：本内容来自平台创作者，博客园系信息发布平台，仅提供信息存储空间服务。\n\n\n好文要顶关注我收藏该文微信分享\n\n[![](https://pic.cnblogs.com/face/sample_face.gif)](https://home.cnblogs.com/u/BeyondTechnology/)\n\n[BeyondTechnology](https://home.cnblogs.com/u/BeyondTechnology/)\n\n[粉丝 \\- 68](https://home.cnblogs.com/u/BeyondTechnology/followers/) [关注 \\- 1](https://home.cnblogs.com/u/BeyondTechnology/followees/)\n\n+加关注\n\n0\n\n0\n\n[升级成为会员](https://cnblogs.vip/)\n\n[«](https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/17794496.html) 上一篇： [pyqt5阻止和删除信号](https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/17794496.html \"发布于 2023-10-28 19:13\")\n\n[»](https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/18924492) 下一篇： [ChromeDriver最新下载地址](https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/18924492 \"发布于 2025-06-11 20:21\")\n\nposted @\n2024-10-10 15:32 [BeyondTechnology](https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology)\n阅读(4399)\n评论(1)\n\n收藏 [举报](https://report.cnblogs.com/?targetLink=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnblogs.com%2FBeyondTech