{"type":"message","id":"e8acb856","parentId":"68f719b6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:44:13.171Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The article mentions `124.71.187.122:7709` was a working IP but stopped working in 2024. The article is from Oct 2024. So the issue is that THS/pytdx server IPs change frequently and the ones I've been trying are likely outdated.\n\nThe article says you need to use the local Tonghuashun client to find the current IP, which requires having the client installed. Since we don't have direct access to the client's settings, this is tricky.\n\nLet me try a few more things:\n1. Try `124.71.187.122` which was mentioned in the article\n2. Try to find other working IPs from a search\n\n\n3. Since this is Mac mini, the user might not have the Tonghuashun client installed, so I should check what other market data sources might work instead","thinkingSignature":"8df41a85ac8c737c803726c4fe86db77ee311f143653e05a14495037d6445e15"},{"type":"text","text":"\n找到线索了——文章提到 `124.71.187.122:7709` 在2024年10月还能用，后来不行了。TDX 服务器 IP 变化频繁，我试的那些都已经过时了。\n\n让我搜一下有没有更新的 IP：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_60v2hlw5i4js_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent && firecrawl search \"pytdx 行情主站 IP 2026\" --limit 5 2>&1 | head -40","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":64557,"output":311,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100074,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776044641182,"responseId":"062b7d6138d97952cf3537da8011a646"}}
{"type":"message","id":"181fb919","parentId":"e8acb856","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:44:15.180Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_60v2hlw5i4js_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"通达信行情地址: · Issue #3 · rainx/pytdx - GitHub\n  URL: https://github.com/rainx/pytdx/issues/3\n  上海电信主站Z1=180.153.18.170:7709. 上海电信主站Z2=180.153.18.171:7709. 上海电信主站Z80=180.153.18.172:80. 北京联通主站Z1=202.108.253.130:7709.\n  Category: github\n\n随笔档案「2024年10月10日」：获取pytdx行情服务器ip和port ...\n  URL: https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/archive/2024/10/10\n  摘要： 之前一直用的api.connect('124.71.187.122', 7709)突然不能用了，调查了一下，给出如下解决方案打开通达信客户端，选项->通讯设置。\n\n获取pytdx行情服务器ip和port - BeyondTechnology - 博客园\n  URL: https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/18456471\n  打开windows任务管理器，找到通达信进程的PID，比如58596。 打开cmd，输入netstat -ano | findstr \"58596\". 端口号7709的IP，即为所选通达信行情主站 ...\n\n部分券商目前的7709端口服务器#51 - rainx/pytdx - GitHub\n  URL: https://github.com/rainx/pytdx/issues/51\n  下面是部分券商目前的TDX普通行情服务器IP，端口都是7709。目前我的网络多数都能PING通，可以参考使用于测试。 安信| 112.95.140.74 安信| 112.95.140.92\n  Category: github\n\n通达信端口问题- 凯帅 - 博客园\n  URL: https://www.cnblogs.com/wukai66/p/19589926\n  获取pytdx行情服务器ip和port ... 打开通达信客户端，选项->通讯设置。 勾掉\"登录时查找最快的主站\"，手动选择\"行情主站\"，点确定。 点击\"选项\"中的\"断开行情主 ..."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1937,"aggregated":"通达信行情地址: · Issue #3 · rainx/pytdx - GitHub\n  URL: https://github.com/rainx/pytdx/issues/3\n  上海电信主站Z1=180.153.18.170:7709. 上海电信主站Z2=180.153.18.171:7709. 上海电信主站Z80=180.153.18.172:80. 北京联通主站Z1=202.108.253.130:7709.\n  Category: github\n\n随笔档案「2024年10月10日」：获取pytdx行情服务器ip和port ...\n  URL: https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/archive/2024/10/10\n  摘要： 之前一直用的api.connect('124.71.187.122', 7709)突然不能用了，调查了一下，给出如下解决方案打开通达信客户端，选项->通讯设置。\n\n获取pytdx行情服务器ip和port - BeyondTechnology - 博客园\n  URL: https://www.cnblogs.com/BeyondTechnology/p/18456471\n  打开windows任务管理器，找到通达信进程的PID，比如58596。 打开cmd，输入netstat -ano | findstr \"58596\". 端口号7709的IP，即为所选通达信行情主站 ...\n\n部分券商目前的7709端口服务器#51 - rainx/pytdx - GitHub\n  URL: https://github.com/rainx/pytdx/issues/51\n  下面是部分券商目前的TDX普通行情服务器IP，端口都是7709。目前我的网络多数都能PING通，可以参考使用于测试。 安信| 112.95.140.74 安信| 112.95.140.92\n  Category: github\n\n通达信端口问题- 凯帅 - 博客园\n  URL: https://www.cnblogs.com/wukai66/p/19589926\n  获取pytdx行情服务器ip和port ... 打开通达信客户端，选项->通讯设置。 勾掉\"登录时查找最快的主站\"，手动选择\"行情主站\"，点确定。 点击\"选项\"中的\"断开行情主 ...","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776044655165}}
{"type":"message","id":"1bfcaed6","parentId":"181fb919","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:44:24.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found some IPs from GitHub issues. Let me try the ones from the pytdx issue page. The ones mentioned are:\n- 180.153.18.170:7709 (上海电信Z1)\n- 180.153.18.171:7709 (上海电信Z2)\n- 202.108.253.130:7709 (北京联通Z1)\n- 112.95.140.74:7709 (安信)\n- 112.95.140.92:7709 (安信)\n\nLet me try these.","thinkingSignature":"867d3ec36b928fe93b6d10175566d6d068b2cd2c06357b1e13d51a9479e2fd9b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g1ujq5pywedz_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom pytdx.hq import TdxHq_API, TDXParams\n\napi = TdxHq_API()\nips = [\n    '180.153.18.170',  # 上海电信Z1\n    '180.153.18.171',  # 上海电信Z2\n    '202.108.253.130', # 北京联通Z1\n    '112.95.140.74',   # 安信\n    '112.95.140.92',   # 安信\n    '124.71.187.122',  # 旧IP\n]\nfor ip in ips:\n    try:\n        if api.connect(ip, 7709):\n            data = api.get_security_bars(TDXParams.QUERY_KL30MIN, 0, '000001', 0, 1)\n            print(f'✅ {ip}:7709 连接成功')\n            if data:\n                print(f'   {data[0].get(\\\"date\\\")} open={data[0].get(\\\"open\\\")}')\n            api.disconnect()\n            break\n        else:\n            print(f'❌ {ip}:7709 连接失败')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'❌ {ip}:7709 {type(e).__name__}: {str(e)[:50]}')\n\" 2>&1","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":65352,"output":453,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101011,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776044655182,"responseId":"062b7d6f2ad35a44d696bbb43e9dd880"}}
