{"type":"message","id":"fc8e631c","parentId":"1f09d15f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:49:06.512Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture:\n\n1. The \"每日自动更新检查\" cron job runs at 03:00 every day\n2. Its `payload.message` is the instruction sent to the AI agent\n3. The AI agent runs `clawhub update --all` and interprets the results\n4. The issue was that the AI was using the wrong logic (simple skip for local changes)\n\nThe problem is not in a script - it's in the **prompt/instruction** that the cron job sends to the AI agent. The AI is interpreting the results of `clawhub update --all` and making decisions based on its understanding.\n\nSo to fix this properly, I need to update the cron job's `payload.message` to give the AI agent better instructions. \n\nI could modify the prompt to be more explicit about how to handle local changes, or I could create a dedicated script at `~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py` that the cron job calls instead, which would give me more control over the logic without relying on the AI's interpretation. the AI agent better instructions on how to interpret the output. I need to modify the cron job's message to guide the AI on analyzing skill update results more intelligently—specifically by having it run my improved script instead of relying on the default `clawhub update --all` interpretation, or by providing clearer guidelines for what to check and how to present the findings.","thinkingSignature":"354b4a0d2039e194276de2f27a47a59301f886063e21dab3af661367978bd262"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了！这个\"每日自动更新检查\"cron（每天03:00）不是调用脚本，而是直接给 AI Agent 发指令。问题出在**指令内容**太粗糙——AI 看到 `clawhub update --all` 的输出后，简单地跳过了所有\"本地有改动\"的 skill。\n\n我来更新这个 cron job 的指令，让它用更智能的逻辑：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ausu7r36ldor_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/update_cron_message.py << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\njobs_path = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/cron/jobs.json'\nwith open(jobs_path) as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# Find and replace the message for the 每日自动更新检查 cron\nold_msg = \"执行以下更新检查并推送摘要：1）运行 `clawhub update --all` 检查已安装 skills 的可更新情况（若因本地改动/可疑技能/缺失技能而跳过，明确写出原因）；2）不要使用 `npm update -g clawdbot@latest --dry-run`，改为只读版本检查：输出本机 `openclaw --version`，再查询 npm 上 `openclaw` 最新版本，判断是否存在新版本；3）不要实际更新 OpenClaw 本体。报告检查结果。\"\n\nnew_msg = \"\"\"执行以下更新检查并推送摘要：\n\n1. **Skills 更新检查**：运行 `python3 ~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/skill_update_check.py`，这个脚本会：\n   - 对\"本地有改动\"的 skill，实际检查改动内容（是否涉及高风险模式如 eval/subprocess/crypto），给出明确建议：保留/更新/review\n   - 区分\"未安装\"vs\"轻量定制\"vs\"有git追踪\"\n   - 报告汇总：⚠️需review、🔄可更新、✅保留本地、⏭未安装\n\n2. **OpenClaw 版本检查**（只读）：运行 `openclaw --version` 查看当前版本，再查询 npm 最新版本（`npm show clawhub version`），判断是否需要升级。**不要执行实际升级**。\n\n3. **汇总输出**：按格式输出结果表格，最后给出明确结论。\n\n推送摘要即可，不需要详细展开每个 skill 的文件列表。\"\"\"\n\n# Find the job and update\njobs = json.loads(content)\nfor job in jobs:\n    if job.get('id') == '55a9fce0-aec0-4dbc-b7cc-c7066c77d995':\n        old_msg_found = job['payload']['message']\n        print(f\"Found message ({len(old_msg_found)} chars):\")\n        print(old_msg_found[:200])\n        job['payload']['message'] = new_msg\n        print(f\"\\nNew message ({len(new_msg)} chars):\")\n        print(new_msg[:200])\n        break\n\nwith open(jobs_path, 'w') as f:\n    json.dump(json.loads(content), f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\nprint(\"\\n✅ jobs.json updated\")\nEOF\npython3 /tmp/update_cron_message.py 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":76945,"output":946,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113097,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776044921969,"responseId":"062b7e7a245978ac3bddd318192ac60c"}}
