{"type":"message","id":"5ccfd6b9","parentId":"acf0184d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:50:46.690Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 09:50:43 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b52f0f1ec1480c4ab0d7142b1697, reply_to:om_x100b52f0e508dcb0b31dccc01dcb454]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52f0f1ec1480c4ab0d7142b1697\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 09:50 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"[message_id=om_x100b52f0e508dcb0b31dccc01dcb454] **结论：所有 TDX 服务器的 7709 端口都关闭了。**\\n\\n```PLAIN_TEXT\\n| IP                     | 7709 端口  |\\n| ---------------------- | -------- |\\n| 180.153.18.170 (上海电信)  | ❌ CLOSED |\\n| 180.153.18.171 (上海电信)  | ❌ CLOSED |\\n| 202.108.253.130 (北京联通) | ❌ CLOSED |\\n| 112.95.140.74 (安信)     | ❌ CLOSED |\\n| 112.95.140.92 (安信)     | ❌ CLOSED |\\n| 124.71.187.122         | ❌ CLOSED |\\n\\n```\\n\\n问题不在你 Mac mini 的防火墙，而是**同花顺服务器本身不再对 7709 端口开放**（可能是商业策略调整，或只接受官方客户端的连接）。\\n**pytdx 实时行情目前不可用。** 你 Mac mini 上的同花顺是通过什么方式获取行情的？如果是走 HTTPS/WebSocket 之类的 HTTP 协议，可能还有救。\"\n}\n```\n\ntdx对应的是通达信，ths对应的是同花顺，你想说的通达信的服务器端口关闭了，对吧？"}],"timestamp":1776045046680}}
{"type":"message","id":"a803dde0","parentId":"5ccfd6b9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:50:58.036Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is correcting me - TDX is TongDaXin (通达信), not TongHuaShun (同花顺). THS = 同花顺, TDX = 通达信. pytdx is for TongDaXin (通达信), not 同花顺.\n\nSo the user is confirming: 通达信's servers have closed port 7709. That's correct - pytdx connects to 通达信 (TongDaXin), not 同花顺 (TongHuaShun).\n\nLet me confirm this correction.","thinkingSignature":"e20c3258ed133a9506e187cfddfcded98bac753308fe195e9600cdcaf0c023ec"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，你说得对，我搞混了：\n\n- **TDX** = 通达信（pytdx 连接的就是这个）\n- **THS** = 同花顺\n\n所以结论是：**通达信的服务器端口 7709 已关闭**，pytdx 用不了不是因为同花顺的问题，而是通达信的行情主站不再对外开放了。\n\n你 Mac mini 上跑的是**同花顺**，那用的是什么接口获取行情？如果是 HTTP/WebSocket 类的，还有救。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":224,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":78989,"totalTokens":114552,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776045046700,"responseId":"062b7ef705d3a10941a1d8f8a1b8a3c5"}}
