gtBx1_um3UotqWF2zZ7OZg)\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n[Permalink: 🚀 快速开始](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md#-%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B)\n\n> ⚠️ 说明（PR-1）：以下历史模块已从代码库移除，并保持默认硬禁用状态：`low_price_bull_*`、`small_cap_*`、`profit_growth_*`、`news_flow_*`（含对应监控数据库文件）。\n\n### 部署方式选择\n\n[Permalink: 部署方式选择](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9)\n\n本系统支持两种部署方式：\n\n- **🐳 Docker部署（推荐）**：一键启动，环境隔离，适合所有用户\n- **💻 本地部署**：传统方式，适合开发者\n\n* * *\n\n## 🐳 方式一：Docker 部署（推荐）⭐️\n\n[Permalink: 🐳 方式一：Docker 部署（推荐）⭐️](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md#-%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%80docker-%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%EF%B8%8F)\n\n### 优势\n\n[Permalink: 优势](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md#%E4%BC%98%E5%8A%BF)\n\n- ✅ 无需配置Python和Node.js环境\n- ✅ 一键启动，开箱即用\n- ✅ 环境隔离，不影响系统\n- ✅ 跨平台支持（Windows/macOS/Linux）\n- ✅ 自动重启，稳定可靠\n\n### 前置要求\n\n[Permalink: 前置要求](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md#%E5%89%8D%E7%BD%AE%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82)\n\n- Docker 20.10+\n- Docker Compose 2.0+（推荐）\n- DeepSeek API Key\n\n### 快速开始\n\n[Permalink: 快速开始](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md#%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B)\n\n#### 1\\. 安装 Docker\n\n[Permalink: 1. 安装 Docker](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md#1-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-docker)\n\n- **Windows/macOS**: 下载安装 [Docker Desktop](https://www.docker.com/products/docker-desktop/)\n- **Linux**:"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7462,"aggregated":"[Skip to content](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md#start-of-content)\n\nYou signed in with another tab or window. [Reload](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md) to refresh your session.You signed out in another tab or window. [Reload](https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/README.md) to refresh your session.You switched accounts on another tab or window. [Reload](https://g