{"type":"message","id":"7c72d967","parentId":"d929b7e0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:54:12.263Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So AI-RXC uses iFinD and Tushare as data sources, not direct THS (同花顺) connection. The \"读取同花顺数据\" in the repo name seems to be a bit misleading - it doesn't directly read from the THS software installed on the user's machine.\n\nThe user's question was about whether THS data can be read locally. Let me check if there's a specific THS interface. Looking at the files - there's `miniqmt_interface.py` which might be related. MiniQMT is a quantitative trading terminal from 里讯 (likely related to THS).\n\nLet me look at the miniqmt_interface.py since MiniQMT is a THS-related product.","thinkingSignature":"a02c24beb6c5ce9a8256b19c125c2f58af597478dff494f5f2999a46aca54ca0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s514fz32saf4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent && firecrawl scrape \"https://github.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/blob/main/miniqmt_interface.py\" --only-main-content -o .firecrawl/miniqmt.md 2>&1 && cat .firecrawl/miniqmt.md | head -80","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":97254,"output":257,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132717,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776045244153,"responseId":"062b7fbcea99a8e05cc7da7f0c501c59"}}
