{"type":"message","id":"a9e86593","parentId":"3a6904b2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:56:31.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting - there's no `xtquant` in the requirements! This means the `miniqmt_interface.py` is a placeholder/TODO in this project. The actual data sources used are tushare, yfinance, and possibly iFinD.\n\nLet me look at the config files and the data source manager more carefully to understand what's actually being used.","thinkingSignature":"9b4b789db976562cdc58eb940fc7564eeea6c9ef874788a6987f03771ad4a64b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uxahsm2uxtvg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 15 \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/main/config.py\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":29661,"output":141,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65008,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776045387160,"responseId":"062b804b68691eedfad214b39bd9c5ea"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0578e892","parentId":"a9e86593","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:56:32.230Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uxahsm2uxtvg_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import os\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\n# 加载环境变量（override=True 强制覆盖已存在的环境变量）\nload_dotenv(override=True)\n\n# DeepSeek API配置\nDEEPSEEK_API_KEY = os.getenv(\"DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\", \"\")\nDEEPSEEK_BASE_URL = os.getenv(\"DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL\", \"https://api.deepseek.com\")\n\n# 其他配置\nTUSHARE_TOKEN = os.getenv(\"TUSHARE_TOKEN\", \"\")\n\n# 股票数据源配置\nDEFAULT_PERIOD = \"1y\"  # 默认获取1年数据\nDEFAULT_INTERVAL = \"1d\"  # 默认日线数据\n\n# MiniQMT量化交易配置\nMINIQMT_CONFIG = {\n    'enabled': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_ENABLED\", \"false\").lower() == \"true\",\n    'account_id': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_ACCOUNT_ID\", \"\"),\n    'host': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_HOST\", \"127.0.0.1\"),\n    'port': int(os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_PORT\", \"58610\")),\n}\n\n# TDX股票数据API配置项目地址github.com/oficcejo/tdx-api\nTDX_CONFIG = {\n    'enabled': os.getenv(\"TDX_ENABLED\", \"false\").lower() == \"true\",\n    'base_url': os.getenv(\"TDX_BASE_URL\", \"http://192.168.1.222:8181\"),\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":548,"aggregated":"import os\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\n# 加载环境变量（override=True 强制覆盖已存在的环境变量）\nload_dotenv(override=True)\n\n# DeepSeek API配置\nDEEPSEEK_API_KEY = os.getenv(\"DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\", \"\")\nDEEPSEEK_BASE_URL = os.getenv(\"DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL\", \"https://api.deepseek.com\")\n\n# 其他配置\nTUSHARE_TOKEN = os.getenv(\"TUSHARE_TOKEN\", \"\")\n\n# 股票数据源配置\nDEFAULT_PERIOD = \"1y\"  # 默认获取1年数据\nDEFAULT_INTERVAL = \"1d\"  # 默认日线数据\n\n# MiniQMT量化交易配置\nMINIQMT_CONFIG = {\n    'enabled': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_ENABLED\", \"false\").lower() == \"true\",\n    'account_id': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_ACCOUNT_ID\", \"\"),\n    'host': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_HOST\", \"127.0.0.1\"),\n    'port': int(os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_PORT\", \"58610\")),\n}\n\n# TDX股票数据API配置项目地址github.com/oficcejo/tdx-api\nTDX_CONFIG = {\n    'enabled': os.getenv(\"TDX_ENABLED\", \"false\").lower() == \"true\",\n    'base_url': os.getenv(\"TDX_BASE_URL\", \"http://192.168.1.222:8181\"),\n}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776045392209}}
{"type":"message","id":"80e9d40f","parentId":"0578e892","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:56:42.790Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! Now I see the key configurations:\n1. `MINIQMT_CONFIG` - MiniQMT connection (disabled by default, needs account_id, host, port 58610)\n2. `TDX_CONFIG` - This is a separate TDX API project (tdx-api by oficcejo) at http://192.168.1.222:8181\n\nThe `tdx-api` project is interesting - it's a separate project that provides a REST API for TDX (通达信) data. Let me check this project.Also, importantly, the data_source_manager shows it uses:\n\n\n- iFinD (if available)\n- Tushare (as backup)\n\nAnd looking at smart_monitor_tdx_data.py, it seems to use a TDX API. So the setup is probably:1. MiniQMT for trading (account-connected)\n2. TDX API (tdx-api by oficcejo) for market data\n3. tushare as backup data source\n\nFor the user's Mac mini with Tonghuashun (not MiniQMT), the options are:\n1. Check if there's a similar REST API server for Tonghuashun\n2. Use tushare as the data source instead\n3. Check if there's a way to connect to Tonghuashun's data via HTTP\n\nI should look into the oficcejo/tdx-api project to understand how it works and whether it could provide the market data connectivity needed.","thinkingSignature":"9a898624469a2e1aa812c21424aa9449b7bebe2651c360b654332e7e943249ec"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vxuflm0389ww_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 15 \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/oficcejo/tdx-api/main/README.md\" 2>/dev/null | head -120","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30115,"output":370,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65691,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776045392231,"responseId":"062b8050039018de1ed257a74fbfbe90"}}
{"type":"message","id":"762a7bcd","parentId":"80e9d40f","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:56:43.365Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vxuflm0389ww_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 📈 TDX通达信股票数据查询系统\n\n> 基于通达信协议的股票数据获取库 + Web可视化界面 + RESTful API\n\n[![Go Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Go-1.22+-00ADD8?style=flat&logo=go)](https://golang.org)\n[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-支持-2496ED?style=flat&logo=docker)](https://www.docker.com)\n[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)\n\n**感谢源作者 [injoyai](https://github.com/injoyai/tdx)，请支持原作者！**\n\n---\n\n## ✨ 功能特性\n\n| 分类 | 功能 |\n|-----|------|\n| **📊 核心功能** | 实时行情（五档盘口）、K线数据（10种周期）、分时数据、股票搜索、批量查询 |\n| **🌐 Web界面** | 现代化UI、ECharts图表、智能搜索、实时刷新 |\n| **🔌 RESTful API** | 32个接口、完整文档、多语言示例、高性能 |\n| **🐳 Docker部署** | 开箱即用、国内镜像加速、跨平台支持 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n### 方式一：Docker部署（推荐）⭐\n\n```bash\n# 克隆项目\ngit clone https://github.com/oficcejo/tdx-api.git\ncd tdx-api\n\n# 启动服务（已配置国内镜像加速）\ndocker-compose up -d\n\n# 访问 http://localhost:8080\n```\n\n**一键启动脚本：**\n- Windows: 双击 `docker-start.bat`\n- Linux/Mac: `chmod +x docker-start.sh && ./docker-start.sh`\n\n### 方式二：源码运行\n\n```bash\n# 前置要求: Go 1.22+\n\n# 1. 下载依赖\ngo mod download\n\n# 2. 进入web目录并运行\ncd web\ngo run .\n\n# 3. 访问 http://localhost:8080\n```\n\n> ⚠️ **注意**: 必须使用 `go run .` 编译所有Go文件，不能使用 `go run server.go`\n\n---\n\n## � API接口列表\n\n### 核心接口\n\n| 接口 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|-----|------|------|\n| `/api/quote` | 五档行情 | `?code=000001` |\n| `/api/kline` | K线数据 | `?code=000001&type=day` |\n| `/api/minute` | 分时数据 | `?code=000001` |\n| `/api/trade` | 分时成交 | `?code=000001` |\n| `/api/search` | 搜索股票 | `?keyword=平安` |\n| `/api/stock-info` | 综合信息 | `?code=000001` |\n\n### 扩展接口\n\n| 接口 | 说明 |\n|-----|------|\n| `/api/codes` | 获取股票代码列表 |\n| `/api/batch-quote` | 批量获取行情 |\n| `/api/kline-history` | 历史K线数据 |\n| `/api/kline-all` | 完整K线数据 |\n| `/api/kline-all/tdx` | TDX源K线数据 |\n| `/api/kline-all/ths` | 同花顺源K线数据（含前复权） |\n| `/api/index` | 指数数据 |\n| `/api/index/all` | 全部指数数据 |\n| `/api/market-stats` | 市场统计 |\n| `/api/market-count` | 市场数量统计 |\n| `/api/stock-codes` | 股票代码 |\n| `/api/etf-codes` | ETF代码 |\n| `/api/etf` | ETF列表 |\n| `/api/trade-history` | 历史成交 |\n| `/api/trade-history/full` | 完整历史成交 |\n| `/api/minute-trade-all` | 全部分时成交 |\n| `/api/workday` | 交易日查询 |\n| `/api/workday/range` | 交易日范围 |\n| `/api/income` | 收益数据 |\n| `/api/tasks/pull-kline` | 创建K线拉取任务 |\n| `/api/tasks/pull-trade` | 创建成交拉取任务 |\n| `/api/tasks` | 任务列表 |\n| `/api/server-status` | 服务器状态 |\n| `/api/health` | 健康检查 |\n\n**完整API文档**: [API_接口文档.md](API_接口文档.md)\n\n---\n\n## � 使用示例\n\n### API调用\n\n```bash\n# 获取实时行情\ncurl \"http://localhost:8080/api/quote?code=000001\"\n\n# 获取日K线\ncurl \"http://localhost:8080/api/kline?code=000001&type=day\"\n\n# 搜索股票\ncurl \"http://localhost:8080/api/search?keyword=平安\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":506,"aggregated":"# 📈 TDX通达信股票数据查询系统\n\n> 基于通达信协议的股票数据获取库 + Web可视化界面 + RESTful API\n\n[![Go Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Go-1.22+-00ADD8?style=flat&logo=go)](https://golang.org)\n[![Docker](https://img.shields.io/badge/Docker-支持-2496ED?style=flat&logo=docker)](https://www.docker.com)\n[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)\n\n**感谢源作者 [injoyai](https://github.com/injoyai/tdx)，请支持原作者！**\n\n---\n\n## ✨ 功能特性\n\n| 分类 | 功能 |\n|-----|------|\n| **📊 核心功能** | 实时行情（五档盘口）、K线数据（10种周期）、分时数据、股票搜索、批量查询 |\n| **🌐 Web界面** | 现代化UI、ECharts图表、智能搜索、实时刷新 |\n| **🔌 RESTful API** | 32个接口、完整文档、多语言示例、高性能 |\n| **🐳 Docker部署** | 开箱即用、国内镜像加速、跨平台支持 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n### 方式一：Docker部署（推荐）⭐\n\n```bash\n# 克隆项目\ngit clone https://github.com/oficcejo/tdx-api.git\ncd tdx-api\n\n# 启动服务（已配置国内镜像加速）\ndocker-compose up -d\n\n# 访问 http://localhost:8080\n```\n\n**一键启动脚本：**\n- Windows: 双击 `docker-start.bat`\n- Linux/Mac: `chmod +x docker-start.sh && ./docker-start.sh`\n\n### 方式二：源码运行\n\n```bash\n# 前置要求: Go 1.22+\n\n# 1. 下载依赖\ngo mod download\n\n# 2. 进入web目录并运行\ncd web\ngo run .\n\n# 3. 访问 http://localhost:8080\n```\n\n> ⚠️ **注意**: 必须使用 `go run .` 编译所有Go文件，不能使用 `go run server.go`\n\n---\n\n## � API接口列表\n\n### 核心接口\n\n| 接口 | 说明 | 示例 |\n|-----|------|------|\n| `/api/quote` | 五档行情 | `?code=000001` |\n| `/api/kline` | K线数据 | `?code=000001&type=day` |\n| `/api/minute` | 分时数据 | `?code=000001` |\n| `/api/trade` | 分时成交 | `?code=000001` |\n| `/api/search` | 搜索股票 | `?keyword=平安` |\n| `/api/stock-info` | 综合信息 | `?code=000001` |\n\n### 扩展接口\n\n| 接口 | 说明 |\n|-----|------|\n| `/api/codes` | 获取股票代码列表 |\n| `/api/batch-quote` | 批量获取行情 |\n| `/api/kline-history` | 历史K线数据 |\n| `/api/kline-all` | 完整K线数据 |\n| `/api/kline-all/tdx` | TDX源K线数据 |\n| `/api/kline-all/ths` | 同花顺源K线数据（含前复权） |\n| `/api/index` | 指数数据 |\n| `/api/index/all` | 全部指数数据 |\n| `/api/market-stats` | 市场统计 |\n| `/api/market-count` | 市场数量统计 |\n| `/api/stock-codes` | 股票代码 |\n| `/api/etf-codes` | ETF代码 |\n| `/api/etf` | ETF列表 |\n| `/api/trade-history` | 历史成交 |\n| `/api/trade-history/full` | 完整历史成交 |\n| `/api/minute-trade-all` | 全部分时成交 |\n| `/api/workday` | 交易日查询 |\n| `/api/workday/range` | 交易日范围 |\n| `/api/income` | 收益数据 |\n| `/api/tasks/pull-kline` | 创建K线拉取任务 |\n| `/api/tasks/pull-trade` | 创建成交拉取任务 |\n| `/api/tasks` | 任务列表 |\n| `/api/server-status` | 服务器状态 |\n| `/api/health` | 健康检查 |\n\n**完整API文档**: [API_接口文档.md](API_接口文档.md)\n\n---\n\n## � 使用示例\n\n### API调用\n\n```bash\n# 获取实时行情\ncurl \"http://localhost:8080/api/quote?code=000001\"\n\n# 获取日K线\ncurl \"http://localhost:8080/api/kline?code=000001&type=day\"\n\n# 搜索股票\ncurl \"http://localhost:8080/api/search?keyword=平安\"","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776045403351}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa729334","parentId":"762a7bcd","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:57:04.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is very promising! The `tdx-api` project (by oficcejo) provides:\n1. RESTful API for stock data\n2. Supports both TDX (通达信) and THS (同花顺) data sources\n3. Can run via Docker on macOS\n4. Has a Web UI\n\nThe key insight is: **`tdx-api` supports THS (同花顺) as a data source**! This means on the Mac mini, if the user has 同花顺 running, the `tdx-api` might be able to connect to it.\n\nBut wait - this runs inside a Docker container. Can Docker on macOS connect to the host's 同花顺 app? In this case, the `tdx-api` would need to either:\n1. Run on a Windows machine where 同花顺 is installed (since Docker on macOS can't easily access host apps)\n\n\n2. Or use the 同花顺 HTTP APIs directly from the data_source_manager.py\n\nLooking at the `localURL.json` we extracted earlier, 同花顺 exposes a bunch of HTTP APIs on the localhost. So I could either use these APIs directly, set up a Windows VM to run both 同花顺 and tdx-api, or check if there's a native macOS solution. Actually, reconsidering this - MiniQMT might have a macOS version or at least a Python package that works across platforms, so let me explore that angle instead.\n\nThe AI-RXC system is pretty flexible with data sources - it supports MiniQMT (which is Windows-only), the tdx-api project (requiring either Windows or Docker), tushare (Chinese market data on any platform), and iFinD (professional tier). Since the user wants to deploy on their Mac mini, tushare is the most straightforward option for market data, though it does require getting an API token first.\n\nFor the Mac mini setup, I'm thinking the best path forward is to get the AI-RXC system running via Docker since it's designed for this, connect it to tushare for market data access, and then tie it together with the MiniQMT configuration for trading execution.\n\nNow I'm realizing there's a complication with the Tonghuashun data source - the `smart_monitor_tdx_data.py` file references a TDX API that might not actually be available on macOS. Let me look more closely at how that module works to understand what data sources we can actually use.","thinkingSignature":"aa5720dff25da12d41eacd003a713c2a676d2e68a6e81d4228a17fe3b5d66078"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yyg6anqt4d7s_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 15 \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/main/smart_monitor_tdx_data.py\" 2>/dev/null | head -80","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":31523,"output":577,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":67306,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776045403366,"responseId":"062b805bca5e9bd11b9558bc0e130a2f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1edae473","parentId":"fa729334","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:57:05.127Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yyg6anqt4d7s_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\n智能盯盘 - TDX数据获取模块\n使用TDX股票数据API接口获取实时行情和技术指标\n\"\"\"\n\nimport logging\nimport requests\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom typing import Dict, Optional\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\n\nclass SmartMonitorTDXDataFetcher:\n    \"\"\"TDX数据获取器\"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, base_url: str = \"http://192.168.1.222:8181\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        初始化TDX数据获取器\n        \n        Args:\n            base_url: TDX API基础地址\n        \"\"\"\n        self.logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n        self.base_url = base_url.rstrip('/')\n        self.timeout = 10  # 请求超时时间（秒）\n        \n        self.logger.info(f\"TDX数据源初始化成功，接口地址: {self.base_url}\")\n    \n    def get_realtime_quote(self, stock_code: str) -> Optional[Dict]:\n        \"\"\"\n        获取实时行情\n        \n        Args:\n            stock_code: 股票代码（如：600519）\n            \n        Returns:\n            实时行情数据\n        \"\"\"\n        try:\n            url = f\"{self.base_url}/api/quote\"\n            params = {'code': stock_code}\n            \n            response = requests.get(url, params=params, timeout=self.timeout)\n            result = response.json()\n            \n            if result['code'] != 0:\n                self.logger.error(f\"TDX获取行情失败: {result.get('message')}\")\n                return None\n            \n            data_list = result.get('data', [])\n            if not data_list:\n                self.logger.warning(f\"TDX未返回股票 {stock_code} 的行情数据\")\n                return None\n            \n            # 获取第一条数据\n            quote_data = data_list[0]\n            k_data = quote_data.get('K', {})\n            \n            # 价格单位转换：厘 -> 元（1元 = 1000厘）\n            current_price = k_data.get('Close', 0) / 1000\n            pre_close = k_data.get('Last', 0) / 1000\n            open_price = k_data.get('Open', 0) / 1000\n            high_price = k_data.get('High', 0) / 1000\n            low_price = k_data.get('Low', 0) / 1000\n            \n            # 成交量单位：手（已是手，无需转换）\n            volume = quote_data.get('TotalHand', 0)\n            \n            # 成交额单位转换：厘 -> 元\n            amount = quote_data.get('Amount', 0) / 1000\n            \n            # 计算涨跌幅\n            change_amount = current_price - pre_close\n            change_pct = (change_amount / pre_close * 100) if pre_close > 0 else 0\n            \n            # 计算换手率（需要流通股本，TDX不提供，暂时设为0）\n            turnover_rate = 0.0\n            \n            # 计算量比（现量/均量，这里用总手数/平均手数估算）\n            vol_ma5 = volume / 1.2  # 简化估算"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":520,"aggregated":"\"\"\"\n智能盯盘 - TDX数据获取模块\n使用TDX股票数据API接口获取实时行情和技术指标\n\"\"\"\n\nimport logging\nimport requests\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom typing import Dict, Optional\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\n\nclass SmartMonitorTDXDataFetcher:\n    \"\"\"TDX数据获取器\"\"\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, base_url: str = \"http://192.168.1.222:8181\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        初始化TDX数据获取器\n        \n        Args:\n            base_url: TDX API基础地址\n        \"\"\"\n        self.logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n        self.base_url = base_url.rstrip('/')\n        self.timeout = 10  # 请求超时时间（秒）\n        \n        self.logger.info(f\"TDX数据源初始化成功，接口地址: {self.base_url}\")\n    \n    def get_realtime_quote(self, stock_code: str) -> Optional[Dict]:\n        \"\"\"\n        获取实时行情\n        \n        Args:\n            stock_code: 股票代码（如：600519）\n            \n        Returns:\n            实时行情数据\n        \"\"\"\n        try:\n            url = f\"{self.base_url}/api/quote\"\n            params = {'code': stock_code}\n            \n            response = requests.get(url, params=params, timeout=self.timeout)\n            result = response.json()\n            \n            if result['code'] != 0:\n                self.logger.error(f\"TDX获取行情失败: {result.get('message')}\")\n                return None\n            \n            data_list = result.get('data', [])\n            if not data_list:\n                self.logger.warning(f\"TDX未返回股票 {stock_code} 的行情数据\")\n                return None\n            \n            # 获取第一条数据\n            quote_data = data_list[0]\n            k_data = quote_data.get('K', {})\n            \n            # 价格单位转换：厘 -> 元（1元 = 1000厘）\n            current_price = k_data.get('Close', 0) / 1000\n            pre_close = k_data.get('Last', 0) / 1000\n            open_price = k_data.get('Open', 0) / 1000\n            high_price = k_data.get('High', 0) / 1000\n            low_price = k_data.get('Low', 0) / 1000\n            \n            # 成交量单位：手（已是手，无需转换）\n            volume = quote_data.get('TotalHand', 0)\n            \n            # 成交额单位转换：厘 -> 元\n            amount = quote_data.get('Amount', 0) / 1000\n            \n            # 计算涨跌幅\n            change_amount = current_price - pre_close\n            change_pct = (change_amount / pre_close * 100) if pre_close > 0 else 0\n            \n            # 计算换手率（需要流通股本，TDX不提供，暂时设为0）\n            turnover_rate = 0.0\n            \n            # 计算量比（现量/均量，这里用总手数/平均手数估算）\n            vol_ma5 = volume / 1.2  # 简化估算","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776045425112}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d4f779d","parentId":"1edae473","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:57:18.828Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture. The system uses:1. `SmartMonitorTDXDataFetcher` - connects to a TDX API server at `http://192.168.1.222:8181` (a local Windows PC on the user's network probably)2. The TDX API server itself can use either TDX (通达信) or THS (同花顺) as its data backend3. For the Mac mini (macOS), the options are:\n\n**Option A: Run tdx-api locally on Mac mini (with THS as backend)**\n- tdx-api supports THS as a data source\n\n\n- But it runs in Docker, and Docker on macOS can't access the THS app running on the host unless THS exposes HTTP APIs\n- The `localURL.json` we found shows THS does expose HTTP APIs!\n\n**Option B: Run tdx-api on a Windows machine on the LAN**\n- This is what the current `192.168.1.222:8181` setup probably does\n- This is actually a good option if they have a Windows PC\n\n**Option C: Use tushare directly**\n- tushare works on any platform\n- AI-RXC already supports it\n- Need to get a TUSHARE_TOKEN\n\nLooking at the `localURL.json` file, THS exposes lots of HTTP APIs on the Mac, but they're designed for the app itself rather than external consumption. The most practical approach would be setting up the tdx-api container on a Windows machine on their network, or getting a tushare token for direct API access on the Mac mini. I should also check if there's a requirements file specific to the Chinese market version.","thinkingSignature":"377b7c8db9f83ff53e21ff98e260815f4f9304954d4ec68ef1f9fef508f01867"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3ejz8g7onucx_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 15 \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wubianshi/AI-RXC/refs/heads/main/docker-compose.yml\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32765,"output":423,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68394,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776045425128,"responseId":"062b807174a122b0c7245efc149c1bbe"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1786ec4a","parentId":"0d4f779d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:57:19.407Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3ejz8g7onucx_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"version: '3.8'\n\nservices:\n  agentsstock:\n    build:\n      context: .\n      dockerfile: Dockerfile\n    container_name: agentsstock1\n    ports:\n      - \"8503:8503\"\n    volumes:\n      # 数据和数据库持久化 - 使用目录挂载而不是文件挂载\n      - ./data:/app/data\n      # 环境变量配置文件\n      - ./.env:/app/.env\n    environment:\n      # 可以在这里设置环境变量，或者使用.env文件\n      - TZ=Asia/Shanghai\n    restart: unless-stopped\n    networks:\n      - agentsstock-network\n    healthcheck:\n      test: [\"CMD\", \"curl\", \"-f\", \"http://localhost:8503/_stcore/health\"]\n      interval: 30s\n      timeout: 10s\n      retries: 3\n      start_period: 60s\n\nnetworks:\n  agentsstock-network:\n    driver: bridge"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":511,"aggregated":"version: '3.8'\n\nservices:\n  agentsstock:\n    build:\n      context: .\n      dockerfile: Dockerfile\n    container_name: agentsstock1\n    ports:\n      - \"8503:8503\"\n    volumes:\n      # 数据和数据库持久化 - 使用目录挂载而不是文件挂载\n      - ./data:/app/data\n      # 环境变量配置文件\n      - ./.env:/app/.env\n    environment:\n      # 可以在这里设置环境变量，或者使用.env文件\n      - TZ=Asia/Shanghai\n    restart: unless-stopped\n    networks:\n      - agentsstock-network\n    healthcheck:\n      test: [\"CMD\", \"curl\", \"-f\", \"http://localhost:8503/_stcore/health\"]\n      interval: 30s\n      timeout: 10s\n      retries: 3\n      start_period: 60s\n\nnetworks:\n  agentsstock-network:\n    driver: bridge","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776045439389}}
