{"type":"message","id":"189665e7","parentId":"13d26464","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:57:23.145Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_vmu5dcb72z6f_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 使用官方Python镜像作为基础镜像\nFROM swr.cn-north-4.myhuaweicloud.com/ddn-k8s/docker.io/python:3.12-slim\n\n# 设置时区环境变量\nENV TZ=Asia/Shanghai\n\n# 替换apt-get源为国内源（阿里源）\nRUN echo \"deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian/ bookworm main\" > /etc/apt/sources.list && \\\n    echo \"deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian/ bookworm-updates main\" >> /etc/apt/sources.list && \\\n    echo \"deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian-security bookworm-security main\" >> /etc/apt/sources.list && \\\n    rm -rf /etc/apt/sources.list.d/* || true\n\n# 设置工作目录\nWORKDIR /app\n\n# 安装基础依赖、中文字体和时区数据\nRUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \\\n    curl \\\n    tar \\\n    xz-utils \\\n    ca-certificates \\\n    fonts-noto-cjk \\\n    fonts-wqy-zenhei \\\n    fonts-wqy-microhei \\\n    fontconfig \\\n    tzdata \\\n    && ln -snf /usr/share/zoneinfo/$TZ /etc/localtime \\\n    && echo $TZ > /etc/timezone \\\n    && fc-cache -fv \\\n    && apt-get clean \\\n    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*\n\n# 安装Node.js（从淘宝镜像下载二进制包，最稳定快速的方案）\nRUN NODE_VERSION=18.20.4 && \\\n    ARCH=$(dpkg --print-architecture) && \\\n    if [ \"$ARCH\" = \"amd64\" ]; then NODE_ARCH=\"x64\"; \\\n    elif [ \"$ARCH\" = \"arm64\" ]; then NODE_ARCH=\"arm64\"; \\\n    else NODE_ARCH=\"$ARCH\"; fi && \\\n    curl -fsSL https://registry.npmmirror.com/-/binary/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/node-v${NODE_VERSION}-linux-${NODE_ARCH}.tar.gz -o /tmp/node.tar.gz && \\\n    tar -xzf /tmp/node.tar.gz -C /usr/local --strip-components=1 && \\\n    rm /tmp/node.tar.gz && \\\n    ln -s /usr/local/bin/node /usr/local/bin/nodejs\n\n# 验证安装\nRUN node --version && npm --version\n\n# 配置npm使用淘宝镜像源\nRUN npm config set registry https://registry.npmmirror.com/\n\n# 复制依赖文件\nCOPY requirements.txt .\n\n# 安装Python依赖（使用清华源，更稳定）\nRUN pip config set global.index-url https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple/ && \\\n    pip config set global.trusted-host pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn && \\\n    pip install --no-cache-dir --default-timeout=1000 -r requirements.txt\n\n# 复制项目文件\nCOPY . .\n\n# 创建必要的目录\nRUN mkdir -p /app/data && chmod 777 /app/data\n\n# 暴露Streamlit默认端口\nEXPOSE 8503\n\n# 设置健康检查\nHEALTHCHECK CMD curl --fail http://localhost:8503/_stcore/health || exit 1\n\n# 启动应用\nCMD [\"streamlit\", \"run\", \"app.py\", \"--server.port=8503\", \"--server.address=0.0.0.0\"]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":500,"aggregated":"# 使用官方Python镜像作为基础镜像\nFROM swr.cn-north-4.myhuaweicloud.com/ddn-k8s/docker.io/python:3.12-slim\n\n# 设置时区环境变量\nENV TZ=Asia/Shanghai\n\n# 替换apt-get源为国内源（阿里源）\nRUN echo \"deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian/ bookworm main\" > /etc/apt/sources.list && \\\n    echo \"deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian/ bookworm-updates main\" >> /etc/apt/sources.list && \\\n    echo \"deb https://mirrors.aliyun.com/debian-security bookworm-security main\" >> /etc/apt/sources.list && \\\n    rm -rf /etc/apt/sources.list.d/* || true\n\n# 设置工作目录\nWORKDIR /app\n\n# 安装基础依赖、中文字体和时区数据\nRUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y \\\n    curl \\\n    tar \\\n    xz-utils \\\n    ca-certificates \\\n    fonts-noto-cjk \\\n    fonts-wqy-zenhei \\\n    fonts-wqy-microhei \\\n    fontconfig \\\n    tzdata \\\n    && ln -snf /usr/share/zoneinfo/$TZ /etc/localtime \\\n    && echo $TZ > /etc/timezone \\\n    && fc-cache -fv \\\n    && apt-get clean \\\n    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*\n\n# 安装Node.js（从淘宝镜像下载二进制包，最稳定快速的方案）\nRUN NODE_VERSION=18.20.4 && \\\n    ARCH=$(dpkg --print-architecture) && \\\n    if [ \"$ARCH\" = \"amd64\" ]; then NODE_ARCH=\"x64\"; \\\n    elif [ \"$ARCH\" = \"arm64\" ]; then NODE_ARCH=\"arm64\"; \\\n    else NODE_ARCH=\"$ARCH\"; fi && \\\n    curl -fsSL https://registry.npmmirror.com/-/binary/node/v${NODE_VERSION}/node-v${NODE_VERSION}-linux-${NODE_ARCH}.tar.gz -o /tmp/node.tar.gz && \\\n    tar -xzf /tmp/node.tar.gz -C /usr/local --strip-components=1 && \\\n    rm /tmp/node.tar.gz && \\\n    ln -s /usr/local/bin/node /usr/local/bin/nodejs\n\n# 验证安装\nRUN node --version && npm --version\n\n# 配置npm使用淘宝镜像源\nRUN npm config set registry https://registry.npmmirror.com/\n\n# 复制依赖文件\nCOPY requirements.txt .\n\n# 安装Python依赖（使用清华源，更稳定）\nRUN pip config set global.index-url https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple/ && \\\n    pip config set global.trusted-host pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn && \\\n    pip install --no-cache-dir --default-timeout=1000 -r requirements.txt\n\n# 复制项目文件\nCOPY . .\n\n# 创建必要的目录\nRUN mkdir -p /app/data && chmod 777 /app/data\n\n# 暴露Streamlit默认端口\nEXPOSE 8503\n\n# 设置健康检查\nHEALTHCHECK CMD curl --fail http://localhost:8503/_stcore/health || exit 1\n\n# 启动应用\nCMD [\"streamlit\", \"run\", \"app.py\", \"--server.port=8503\", \"--server.address=0.0.0.0\"]","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776045443129}}
{"type":"message","id":"d45b3192","parentId":"189665e7","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:57:45.702Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a very clear picture. Let me summarize what I've learned and propose a plan:\n\n**The AI-RXC System:**\n- Streamlit-based multi-agent stock analysis system\n- Deploys via Docker (docker-compose)\n- Data sources: TDX API (tdx-api server on Windows), tushare, iFinD\n- Has modules for: stage1 (intraday), stage2 (selection), review center, eod watch, sector strategy, etc.\n\n**Current Setup of User:**\n- Mac mini running Tonghuashun (同花顺) app\n- AI-RXC wants to connect to TDX API server at 192.168.1.222:8181\n\n\n- The TDX API server runs on a Windows machine on the LAN with either TDX or THS installed, providing market data via REST API\n\n**For the Mac Mini (macOS), there are several possible setups:**\n\n**Option 1 (Recommended): Keep existing Windows TDX API server**\n- If they already have a Windows PC running TDX or THS with the tdx-api server at 192.168.1.222, just configure AI-RXC to use it\n\n**Option 2: Deploy tdx-api on Mac mini via Docker + THS**\n- The tdx-api supports THS as a data source\n- Docker on macOS can't directly access THS running on the host, but THS exposes HTTP APIs that could potentially be containerized\n- This is getting complex though\n\n**Option 3: Use tushare as primary data source**\n- Works on any platform\n- AI-RXC already supports it\n- Need TUSHARE_TOKEN (free to get)\n\n**Option 4: Set up a Windows VM on Mac mini**\n- If they have a Windows VM or Parallels/VMware Fusion, could run the full stack on Windows\n\n**My recommended approach:**\n\nFor a Mac mini setup without a Windows VM, I should either get a TUSHARE_TOKEN for cloud-based data or look for a native macOS solution like InfoROC's APIs.\n\nLet me look into what options are actually viable on macOS and give them a straightforward answer. Actually, the most practical path is probably to run the tdx-api server on whatever Windows machine they have available, then have AI-RXC connect to it as the data backend. Alternatively, I could set up a Docker container for AI-RXC on the Mac mini and configure it with tushare as the primary data source.","thinkingSignature":"d7e2c3a7ec98d80fd2eb839aaf0f89cd9e1a30ecd0aad44fdd6f7220d4be7fd6"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我完全理解这个项目了。让我给你一个清晰的部署方案：\n\n---\n\n## 情况分析\n\n你的 Mac mini 上跑的是**同花顺**，而 AI-RXC 的数据架构是：\n\n```\nAI-RXC (Mac mini Docker)\n    ↓ HTTP 请求\ntdx-api 服务器 (通常是 Windows PC，端口 8181)\n    ↓ 通达信/同花顺 协议\n行情数据\n```\n\n当前配置指向的是 `192.168.1.222:8181`（局域网内某台 Windows 电脑）。\n\n**问题**：你的 Mac mini 上**没有 Windows 虚拟机，也没有 TDX API 服务器**。\n\n---\n\n## 推荐方案：Mac mini 本地部署\n\n分两步走：\n\n### 第一步：获取 TUSHARE Token（免费，5分钟搞定）\n\n1. 打开 https://tushare.pro/register?reg=485  注册账号\n2. 申请一个 Token（免费个人版足够）\n3. 告诉我你的 Token，我帮你写入配置\n\n### 第二步：在 Mac mini 上启动 AI-RXC\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m02n2objan6v_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"which docker && docker --version 2>/dev/null; ls ~/Library/Containers/com.docker.docker* 2>/dev/null | head -3","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":34208,"output":789,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70203,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776045443147,"responseId":"062b80833ade87ee17e7c686cab7099c"}}
