{"type":"message","id":"e7e2d635","parentId":"5f2bae73","timestamp":"2026-04-13T01:57:52.436Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Docker is installed and running on the Mac mini. Let me now set up the deployment. I'll:\n\n1. Clone the AI-RXC repo to the Mac mini\n2. Configure the .env file with TUSHARE_TOKEN\n3. Start it with docker-compose\n\nBut first, let me check if there's already a deployment of this on the Mac mini, and also understand what data sources the user currently uses for their investment research system.\n\nLet me also check the disk space and existing setup.","thinkingSignature":"d5622d66a509826679e3b97b81df9b26ddf1c2355ea3463061bdfa863435858d"},{"type":"text","text":"Docker 已经在 Mac mini 上装好了。现在让我把 AI-RXC 部署到你本地。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_giop2cbqqmwd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"df -h / | tail -1; free -h 2>/dev/null || vm_stat 2>/dev/null | head -5","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":35043,"output":182,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70431,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776045466014,"responseId":"062b809a5aaab4bbafeec4eaf500d21e"}}
