{"type":"message","id":"43d393d6","parentId":"a13e1236","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:14:13.167Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 10:14:10 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b52f0a42e64f4c4e1738ecf1b73c, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52f0a42e64f4c4e1738ecf1b73c\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 10:02 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n收到，已直接执行并交付补丁包。\n**已完成产物**\n1. deliverables/thsdata-realtime-fix-20260318/patches/0001-thsdata-compat-with-new-thsdk.patch\n- 作用：把 thsdata 适配到新版 thsdk（THS API），恢复 Quote/FuquanNo/KlineDay 等兼容用法。\n2. deliverables/thsdata-realtime-fix-20260318/patches/0002-thsdk-fix-darwin-arm64-arch-check.patch\n- 作用：修复 Apple Silicon 下错误加载 amd64 动态库的问题。\n3. deliverables/thsdata-realtime-fix-20260318/logs/smoke-test.log\n- 作用：实测验收日志（真实拉到行情数据）。\n4. deliverables/thsdata-realtime-fix-20260318/[README.md](http://readme.md/)\n- 作用：补丁说明与应用方式。\n**提交记录**\n- commit: 16fe5f9\n- message: add thsdata/thsdk realtime data compatibility patches and smoke-test log\n**验收关键结果（来自 smoke-test.log）**\n- market_data_cn ok= True\n- bars rows= 4（日K正常返回）\n- call_auction rows= 61（集合竞价数据正常返回）\n这是之前周到给我修复的同花顺的连接，你看看还能用不？"}],"timestamp":1776046453158}}
