{"type":"message","id":"5cb99295","parentId":"2621871e","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:14:38.604Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ls6y0yi8bt5u_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# thsdata 实时数据修复交付（2026-03-18）\n\n## 结论\n原仓库可通过补丁方式恢复可用：\n1) thsdata 适配新版 thsdk API\n2) thsdk 修复 Darwin arm64 动态库架构判断\n\n## 产物\n- `patches/0001-thsdata-compat-with-new-thsdk.patch`\n- `patches/0002-thsdk-fix-darwin-arm64-arch-check.patch`\n- `apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh`（一键应用脚本）\n- `logs/smoke-test.log`\n\n## 一键应用\n```bash\ncd deliverables/thsdata-realtime-fix-20260318\nbash apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh\n```\n\n常用参数：\n```bash\nbash apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh --workdir /tmp/ths-fix\nbash apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh --skip-smoke\nbash apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh --dry-run\n```\n\n## 手动应用（示例）\n```bash\n# thsdk\npip download --no-binary :all: --no-deps thsdk==1.7.15\n# 解压后应用 0002 patch 并安装\n\n# thsdata\ngit clone https://github.com/jsczsyx969/thsdata.git\ncd thsdata\ngit apply /path/to/0001-thsdata-compat-with-new-thsdk.patch\npip install -e .\n```\n\n## 验收摘要\n详见 `logs/smoke-test.log`，核心结果：\n- `market_data_cn ok=True`\n- `security_bars` 返回有效日K\n- `call_auction` 返回集合竞价数据"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":30,"aggregated":"# thsdata 实时数据修复交付（2026-03-18）\n\n## 结论\n原仓库可通过补丁方式恢复可用：\n1) thsdata 适配新版 thsdk API\n2) thsdk 修复 Darwin arm64 动态库架构判断\n\n## 产物\n- `patches/0001-thsdata-compat-with-new-thsdk.patch`\n- `patches/0002-thsdk-fix-darwin-arm64-arch-check.patch`\n- `apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh`（一键应用脚本）\n- `logs/smoke-test.log`\n\n## 一键应用\n```bash\ncd deliverables/thsdata-realtime-fix-20260318\nbash apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh\n```\n\n常用参数：\n```bash\nbash apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh --workdir /tmp/ths-fix\nbash apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh --skip-smoke\nbash apply_thsdata_realtime_fix.sh --dry-run\n```\n\n## 手动应用（示例）\n```bash\n# thsdk\npip download --no-binary :all: --no-deps thsdk==1.7.15\n# 解压后应用 0002 patch 并安装\n\n# thsdata\ngit clone https://github.com/jsczsyx969/thsdata.git\ncd thsdata\ngit apply /path/to/0001-thsdata-compat-with-new-thsdk.patch\npip install -e .\n```\n\n## 验收摘要\n详见 `logs/smoke-test.log`，核心结果：\n- `market_data_cn ok=True`\n- `security_bars` 返回有效日K\n- `call_auction` 返回集合竞价数据","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776046478596}}
