{"type":"message","id":"07ef7e0d","parentId":"00b93de3","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:16:24.778Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The thsdata library is working perfectly! It connected to the THS server and successfully retrieved:\n1. Real-time market data for USZA300033 (同花顺/THS)\n2. K-line data (bars)\n3. Call auction data\n\nNow I should also verify it works with a regular A-share stock like 贵州茅台 (600519). And then I should integrate this with the AI-RXC Docker container.Let me also test with a regular A-share stock.","thinkingSignature":"9b91178fa055b38f067bc4af6e8f83192e103941759f8f48e02b072c4a15fbe7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ezdvcrczq40c_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom thsdata import Quote, FuquanNo, KlineDay\nimport datetime\n\nq = Quote()\n\n# 测试A股\nstocks = ['600519', '000001', '300750']\nfor code in stocks:\n    md = q.ths.market_data_cn(code)\n    name = md.data[0].get('名称', 'N/A') if md.data else 'N/A'\n    price = md.data[0].get('价格', 0) if md.data else 0\n    print(f'{code} {name}: {price}')\n\nq.disconnect()\nprint('✅ A股行情获取成功！')\n\" 2>&1","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":91478,"output":287,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":126971,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776046575145,"responseId":"062b84ef2cd087f9209c979284120316"}}
