{"type":"message","id":"1a5e497e","parentId":"f2683989","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:16:40.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The THS data for A-share stocks isn't returning price data with just the stock code. It might need a market prefix. Let me check how the code should be formatted. Looking at the smoke test, USZA300033 was used for 同花顺 (THS/300033). \n\nLet me check the correct format for A-share stocks. In China stock market:- 上海A股: USZA600519 (SHSE)\n- 深圳A股: USZA000001 (SZSE)\n- 创业板: USZA300750 (SZSE GEM)\n\nThe `USZA` prefix might be for the THS API format. Let me try with the correct format.","thinkingSignature":"80efa9b1b2c530ba45fd7acbe2b5790743d4603cd413d21cd616b61bfc431a2d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l6utncac65nj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom thsdata import Quote, FuquanNo, KlineDay\nimport datetime\n\nq = Quote()\n\n# 测试A股 - THS格式是 USZA + 代码\nstocks = ['USZA600519', 'USZA000001', 'USZA300750', 'USZA300033']\nfor code in stocks:\n    md = q.ths.market_data_cn(code)\n    name = md.data[0].get('名称', 'N/A') if md.data else 'N/A'\n    price = md.data[0].get('价格', 0) if md.data else 0\n    change = md.data[0].get('涨跌额', 0) if md.data else 0\n    pct = md.data[0].get('涨跌幅', 0) if md.data else 0\n    print(f'{code} {name}: {price} ({change:+.2f} {pct:+.2f}%)')\n\nq.disconnect()\n\" 2>&1 | grep -v \"INFO\\|WARNING\\|account\\|mac\\|失效\\|建议\\|配置\\|临时\\|游客\"","yieldMs":15000,"timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92082,"output":415,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127703,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776046587959,"responseId":"062b84fc8eba0986a8b35a6f1117f3a6"}}
