{"type":"message","id":"bc750b18","parentId":"32cfcd30","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:16:57.424Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that 平安银行 and 宁德时代 and 同花顺 are returning data, but 600519 (贵州茅台) is not found. Let me check the correct THS code for 贵州茅台. Actually, the issue might be that the market prefix is wrong. Let me check - in THS format:- 上海A股: HSA (not USZA)- 深圳A股: USA (not USZA)- 创业板: USA (for GEM)\n\nWait, looking at the format again - \"USZA\" might mean different things. Let me check with the actual format used by the THS API. The smoke test used USZA300033 for 同花顺, which is correct. \n\n600519 is definitely 贵州茅台 on the Shanghai market, but the THS format might use a different prefix like HSA instead of USZA. Let me try that variation.","thinkingSignature":"eabe805f7b704fc084a264897def1d84417e46d73f467564b18c2c77a7af6cc9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5ifc7cn9hocu_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nfrom thsdata import Quote\nq = Quote()\n# 试试不同前缀格式\ncodes = ['HSA600519', 'SHA600519', 'SH600519', 'USA000001']\nfor c in codes:\n    md = q.ths.market_data_cn(c)\n    if md.data:\n        print(f'{c}: {md.data[0].get(\\\"名称\\\")} {md.data[0].get(\\\"价格\\\")}')\nq.disconnect()\n\" 2>&1 | grep -E \"HSA|SHA|SH|USA\" | grep -v \"INFO\\|WARNING\"","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":92593,"output":353,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128152,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776046605151,"responseId":"062b850d217c9ac5df9f70f6732023e6"}}
