{"type":"message","id":"55e03abb","parentId":"bd85e6f8","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:17:30.110Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 10:17:28 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b52f0bb2022d4c4c85678356c9b3]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52f0bb2022d4c4c85678356c9b3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 10:05 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n在本地部署：https://github.com/bensema/gotdxhttps://github.com/bensema/gotdxhttps://github.com/bensema/gotdx"}],"timestamp":1776046650100}}
{"type":"message","id":"24959ba2","parentId":"55e03abb","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:17:37.868Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to deploy this `gotdx` project locally. Let me first look at what this project does.","thinkingSignature":"db71776cd74b04b652fd45d52f2fa6f357dfbde5639f3ef31249bb1825035450"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_u6t2f6c8bzjb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 15 \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/bensema/gotdx/main/README.md\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":91,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":92108,"totalTokens":127538,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776046650123,"responseId":"062b853af68ac74c2c931b18f855bc37"}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc03b88d","parentId":"24959ba2","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:17:38.468Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_u6t2f6c8bzjb_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# gotdx\n\n<p align=\"center\">通达信行情协议的 Go 客户端，覆盖主行情、扩展市场、MAC 板块/统一行情、F10/文件接口，以及一个可直接运行的 Web Viewer。</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"#quickstart\">快速开始</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#capabilities\">能力概览</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#examples\">示例</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#viewer\">Web Viewer</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#api\">API 速览</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#testing\">测试</a> ·\n  <a href=\"TdxProtocol.md\">协议文档</a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Go-1.26%2B-00ADD8?logo=go&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Go 1.26+\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Markets-Main%20%2F%20Extended-123B67\" alt=\"Markets\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/MAC-Supported-0F766E\" alt=\"MAC\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/WebViewer-Built--in-C86B36\" alt=\"Web Viewer\">\n</p>\n\n`gotdx` 把通达信协议里常用的查询能力整理成更偏 Go 的调用方式。你可以直接查主行情和扩展市场的快照、K 线、分时、逐笔，也可以继续往下钻到 F10、财务、板块文件、扩展表格和 MAC 板块协议；如果只是想先看接口返回长什么样，仓库里还带了一个可以直接打开的网页查看器。\n\n## 为什么用 gotdx\n\n- 一个 `Client` 同时管理主站和扩展市场，适合做统一监控和跨市场抓取。\n- 提供两套入口：高阶统一接口 `Stock* / Ex* / MAC*`，以及面向协议细节的底层 `Get* / ExGet*`。\n- 地址池、超时、重试都可配，适合对接不稳定的真实行情站点。\n- 内置从 `opentdx` 搬运的主站、扩展、MAC、券商 host/IP 列表，并支持 TCP 测速选最快节点。\n- 自带 30+ 个示例，覆盖从列表、快照、K 线、分时到 F10、板块、扩展表格。\n- 自带 `cmd/webviewer`，不写代码也能直接调方法、填参数、看返回字段。\n- 已整理 `opentdx` 对照文档，便于继续补协议、核字段和排查差异。\n\n<a id=\"quickstart\"></a>\n## 快速开始\n\n### 安装\n\n```bash\ngo get github.com/bensema/gotdx\n```\n\n### 最小示例\n\n```go\npackage main\n\nimport (\n\t\"log\"\n\n\t\"github.com/bensema/gotdx\"\n)\n\nfunc main() {\n\tmainHosts := gotdx.MainHostAddresses()\n\texHosts := gotdx.ExHostAddresses()\n\n\tclient := gotdx.New(\n\t\tgotdx.WithTCPAddress(mainHosts[0]),\n\t\tgotdx.WithTCPAddressPool(mainHosts[1:]...),\n\t\tgotdx.WithExTCPAddress(exHosts[0]),\n\t\tgotdx.WithExTCPAddressPool(exHosts[1:]...),\n\t\tgotdx.WithAutoSelectFastest(true),\n\t\tgotdx.WithTimeoutSec(6),\n\t)\n\tdefer client.Disconnect()\n\n\tstocks, err := client.StockQuotesDetail(\n\t\t[]uint8{gotdx.MarketSZ, gotdx.MarketSH},\n\t\t[]string{\"000001\", \"600519\"},\n\t)\n\tif err != nil {\n\t\tlog.Fatal(err)\n\t}\n\tfor _, item := range stocks {\n\t\tlog.Printf(\"stock code=%s price=%.2f turnover=%.2f%%\", item.Code, item.Price, item.Turnover)\n\t}\n\n\texQuotes, err := client.ExQuotes(\n\t\t[]uint8{gotdx.ExCategoryUSStock},\n\t\t[]string{\"TSLA\"},\n\t)\n\tif err != nil {\n\t\tlog.Fatal(err)\n\t}\n\tfor _, item := range exQuotes {\n\t\tlog.Printf(\"ex: %+v\", item)\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n### 从哪套 API 开始\n\n- 想尽快拿到业务数据：优先用 `Stock* / Ex* / MAC*` 统一高阶入口。\n- 想逐个协议排查字段：用 `Get* / ExGet* / GetMAC*` 底层接口。\n- 想先确认请求参数和返回格式：直接运行 `go run ./cmd/webviewer`。\n\n### 内置 Host 列表与测速\n\n```go"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":569,"aggregated":"# gotdx\n\n<p align=\"center\">通达信行情协议的 Go 客户端，覆盖主行情、扩展市场、MAC 板块/统一行情、F10/文件接口，以及一个可直接运行的 Web Viewer。</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"#quickstart\">快速开始</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#capabilities\">能力概览</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#examples\">示例</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#viewer\">Web Viewer</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#api\">API 速览</a> ·\n  <a href=\"#testing\">测试</a> ·\n  <a href=\"TdxProtocol.md\">协议文档</a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Go-1.26%2B-00ADD8?logo=go&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Go 1.26+\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Markets-Main%20%2F%20Extended-123B67\" alt=\"Markets\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/MAC-Supported-0F766E\" alt=\"MAC\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/WebViewer-Built--in-C86B36\" alt=\"Web Viewer\">\n</p>\n\n`gotdx` 把通达信协议里常用的查询能力整理成更偏 Go 的调用方式。你可以直接查主行情和扩展市场的快照、K 线、分时、逐笔，也可以继续往下钻到 F10、财务、板块文件、扩展表格和 MAC 板块协议；如果只是想先看接口返回长什么样，仓库里还带了一个可以直接打开的网页查看器。\n\n## 为什么用 gotdx\n\n- 一个 `Client` 同时管理主站和扩展市场，适合做统一监控和跨市场抓取。\n- 提供两套入口：高阶统一接口 `Stock* / Ex* / MAC*`，以及面向协议细节的底层 `Get* / ExGet*`。\n- 地址池、超时、重试都可配，适合对接不稳定的真实行情站点。\n- 内置从 `opentdx` 搬运的主站、扩展、MAC、券商 host/IP 列表，并支持 TCP 测速选最快节点。\n- 自带 30+ 个示例，覆盖从列表、快照、K 线、分时到 F10、板块、扩展表格。\n- 自带 `cmd/webviewer`，不写代码也能直接调方法、填参数、看返回字段。\n- 已整理 `opentdx` 对照文档，便于继续补协议、核字段和排查差异。\n\n<a id=\"quickstart\"></a>\n## 快速开始\n\n### 安装\n\n```bash\ngo get github.com/bensema/gotdx\n```\n\n### 最小示例\n\n```go\npackage main\n\nimport (\n\t\"log\"\n\n\t\"github.com/bensema/gotdx\"\n)\n\nfunc main() {\n\tmainHosts := gotdx.MainHostAddresses()\n\texHosts := gotdx.ExHostAddresses()\n\n\tclient := gotdx.New(\n\t\tgotdx.WithTCPAddress(mainHosts[0]),\n\t\tgotdx.WithTCPAddressPool(mainHosts[1:]...),\n\t\tgotdx.WithExTCPAddress(exHosts[0]),\n\t\tgotdx.WithExTCPAddressPool(exHosts[1:]...),\n\t\tgotdx.WithAutoSelectFastest(true),\n\t\tgotdx.WithTimeoutSec(6),\n\t)\n\tdefer client.Disconnect()\n\n\tstocks, err := client.StockQuotesDetail(\n\t\t[]uint8{gotdx.MarketSZ, gotdx.MarketSH},\n\t\t[]string{\"000001\", \"600519\"},\n\t)\n\tif err != nil {\n\t\tlog.Fatal(err)\n\t}\n\tfor _, item := range stocks {\n\t\tlog.Printf(\"stock code=%s price=%.2f turnover=%.2f%%\", item.Code, item.Price, item.Turnover)\n\t}\n\n\texQuotes, err := client.ExQuotes(\n\t\t[]uint8{gotdx.ExCategoryUSStock},\n\t\t[]string{\"TSLA\"},\n\t)\n\tif err != nil {\n\t\tlog.Fatal(err)\n\t}\n\tfor _, item := range exQuotes {\n\t\tlog.Printf(\"ex: %+v\", item)\n\t}\n}\n```\n\n### 从哪套 API 开始\n\n- 想尽快拿到业务数据：优先用 `Stock* / Ex* / MAC*` 统一高阶入口。\n- 想逐个协议排查字段：用 `Get* / ExGet* / GetMAC*` 底层接口。\n- 想先确认请求参数和返回格式：直接运行 `go run ./cmd/webviewer`。\n\n### 内置 Host 列表与测速\n\n```go","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776046658458}}
