{"type":"message","id":"109b6d5f","parentId":"0f501fa4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:20:57.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Excellent! The gotdx webviewer is working and returning real-time stock data! Let me also test the connection and see what it looks like.\n\nNow let me:\n1. Install the webviewer to a permanent location\n2. Create a launchd service for it (or write a start/stop script)\n3. Report the status to the user\n\nThe gotdx webviewer is working on port 8089. It provides real-time A-share market data through the TDX protocol. This is perfect for the user's Mac mini!\n\nLet me also install it to a permanent path and set up auto-start.","thinkingSignature":"681b8ded8822922694dd56148474977531e5e8d8f5e31e1830f18dee78da99ee"},{"type":"text","text":"🎉 **gotdx 部署成功！实测行情正常！**\n\n```\n平安银行(000001): 11.04元 (-0.05)\n贵州茅台(600519): 1441.01元 (-12.95)\n响应时间: 224ms\n```\n\n**Web 界面：** http://127.0.0.1:8089\n\n现在让我把它安装到永久路径并设置开机自启：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5umc05w6abai_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/bin && cp /tmp/gotdx/webviewer ~/bin/ && chmod +x ~/bin/webviewer && echo \"Installed to ~/bin/webviewer\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":102498,"output":278,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137982,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776046847714,"responseId":"062b86004b2292396290c20aba15bf0e"}}
