{"type":"message","id":"58e9f501","parentId":"c5caa40d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:22:06.157Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to integrate gotdx API into AI-RXC as a data source. Let me first check how AI-RXC's data source is currently configured, and then modify it to use gotdx API.\n\nLet me look at the data_source_manager.py and config.py to understand the current data source architecture.","thinkingSignature":"b26eabb47171cd318912aa6ffad8159374a2403ac0e9e859f72fda9294ccf6e3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_68dd3fq13qyd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/AI-RXC/data_source_manager.py 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":115,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":103874,"totalTokens":139328,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776046919517,"responseId":"062b86484a16173dab9de951806d496c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b35c7adb","parentId":"58e9f501","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:22:06.251Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_68dd3fq13qyd_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\n数据源管理器\n实现iFinD和tushare的自动切换机制\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\n# 加载环境变量\nload_dotenv()\n\n\nclass DataSourceManager:\n    \"\"\"数据源管理器 - 实现iFinD与tushare自动切换\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.tushare_token = os.getenv(\"TUSHARE_TOKEN\", \"\")\n        self.tushare_available = False\n        self.tushare_api = None\n\n        # 初始化tushare\n        if self.tushare_token:\n            try:\n                import tushare as ts\n\n                ts.set_token(self.tushare_token)\n                self.tushare_api = ts.pro_api()\n                self.tushare_available = True\n                print(\"✅ Tushare数据源初始化成功\")\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"⚠️ Tushare数据源初始化失败: {e}\")\n                self.tushare_available = False\n        else:\n            print(\"ℹ️ 未配置Tushare Token，将仅使用iFinD数据源\")\n\n    def get_stock_hist_data(self, symbol, start_date=None, end_date=None, adjust=\"qfq\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取股票历史数据（优先iFinD，失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码（6位数字）\n            start_date: 开始日期（格式：'20240101'或'2024-01-01'）\n            end_date: 结束日期\n            adjust: 复权类型（'qfq'前复权, 'hfq'后复权, ''不复权）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 包含日期、开盘、收盘、最高、最低、成交量等列\n        \"\"\"\n        # 标准化日期格式\n        if start_date:\n            start_date = start_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        if end_date:\n            end_date = end_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        else:\n            end_date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n        # 优先使用iFinD\n        try:\n            from ifind_client import history_quotes\n\n            print(f\"[iFinD] 正在获取 {symbol} 的历史数据...\")\n            indicators = \"open,high,low,close,volume,amount,pct_chg,turnover\"\n            df = history_quotes(\n                symbol, indicators, start_date, end_date, params=f\"adj={adjust}\"\n            )\n\n            if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                df = df.rename(\n                    columns={\n                        \"time\": \"date\",\n                        \"date\": \"date\",\n                        \"pct_chg\": \"pct_change\",\n                    }\n                )\n                if \"date\" in df.columns:\n                    df[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df[\"date\"])\n                print(f\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取 {len(df)} 条数据\")\n                return df\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的历史数据（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                # 转换股票代码格式（添加市场后缀）\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n\n                # 转换复权类型\n                adj_dict = {\"qfq\": \"qfq\", \"hfq\": \"hfq\", \"\": None}\n                adj = adj_dict.get(adjust, \"qfq\")\n\n                # 格式化日期\n                start = (\n                    f\"{start_date[:4]}-{start_date[4:6]}-{start_date[6:]}\"\n                    if start_date\n                    else None"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":27,"aggregated":"\"\"\"\n数据源管理器\n实现iFinD和tushare的自动切换机制\n\"\"\"\n\nimport os\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\n# 加载环境变量\nload_dotenv()\n\n\nclass DataSourceManager:\n    \"\"\"数据源管理器 - 实现iFinD与tushare自动切换\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.tushare_token = os.getenv(\"TUSHARE_TOKEN\", \"\")\n        self.tushare_available = False\n        self.tushare_api = None\n\n        # 初始化tushare\n        if self.tushare_token:\n            try:\n                import tushare as ts\n\n                ts.set_token(self.tushare_token)\n                self.tushare_api = ts.pro_api()\n                self.tushare_available = True\n                print(\"✅ Tushare数据源初始化成功\")\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"⚠️ Tushare数据源初始化失败: {e}\")\n                self.tushare_available = False\n        else:\n            print(\"ℹ️ 未配置Tushare Token，将仅使用iFinD数据源\")\n\n    def get_stock_hist_data(self, symbol, start_date=None, end_date=None, adjust=\"qfq\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取股票历史数据（优先iFinD，失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码（6位数字）\n            start_date: 开始日期（格式：'20240101'或'2024-01-01'）\n            end_date: 结束日期\n            adjust: 复权类型（'qfq'前复权, 'hfq'后复权, ''不复权）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 包含日期、开盘、收盘、最高、最低、成交量等列\n        \"\"\"\n        # 标准化日期格式\n        if start_date:\n            start_date = start_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        if end_date:\n            end_date = end_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        else:\n            end_date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n        # 优先使用iFinD\n        try:\n            from ifind_client import history_quotes\n\n            print(f\"[iFinD] 正在获取 {symbol} 的历史数据...\")\n            indicators = \"open,high,low,close,volume,amount,pct_chg,turnover\"\n            df = history_quotes(\n                symbol, indicators, start_date, end_date, params=f\"adj={adjust}\"\n            )\n\n            if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                df = df.rename(\n                    columns={\n                        \"time\": \"date\",\n                        \"date\": \"date\",\n                        \"pct_chg\": \"pct_change\",\n                    }\n                )\n                if \"date\" in df.columns:\n                    df[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df[\"date\"])\n                print(f\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取 {len(df)} 条数据\")\n                return df\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的历史数据（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                # 转换股票代码格式（添加市场后缀）\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n\n                # 转换复权类型\n                adj_dict = {\"qfq\": \"qfq\", \"hfq\": \"hfq\", \"\": None}\n                adj = adj_dict.get(adjust, \"qfq\")\n\n                # 格式化日期\n                start = (\n                    f\"{start_date[:4]}-{start_date[4:6]}-{start_date[6:]}\"\n                    if start_date\n                    else None","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776046926242}}
{"type":"message","id":"9eb8f8a4","parentId":"b35c7adb","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:22:10.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me see the rest of this file and understand the full data source architecture.","thinkingSignature":"3080db5ba99e7cd7c68e926c7f27fce0394c8d79bb462ce11d3bccf13d788fb2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_k5sdbv2q3tii_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/AI-RXC/data_source_manager.py 2>/dev/null | tail -200","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":104938,"output":69,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":140213,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776046926252,"responseId":"062b864eeac4d2cc465b4925267595f2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"141cb968","parentId":"9eb8f8a4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:22:10.096Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_k5sdbv2q3tii_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"流通市值\", info.get(\"circulating_market_cap\")\n                )\n                print(\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取基本信息\")\n                return info\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的基本信息（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n                df = self.tushare_api.stock_basic(\n                    ts_code=ts_code,\n                    fields=\"ts_code,name,area,industry,market,list_date\",\n                )\n\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    info[\"name\"] = df.iloc[0][\"name\"]\n                    info[\"industry\"] = df.iloc[0][\"industry\"]\n                    info[\"market\"] = df.iloc[0][\"market\"]\n                    info[\"list_date\"] = df.iloc[0][\"list_date\"]\n\n                    print(\"[Tushare] ✅ 成功获取基本信息\")\n                    return info\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        return info\n\n    def get_realtime_quotes(self, symbol):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取实时行情数据（优先iFinD，失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码\n\n        Returns:\n            dict: 实时行情数据\n        \"\"\"\n        quotes = {}\n\n        # 优先使用iFinD\n        try:\n            from ifind_client import realtime_quotes\n\n            print(f\"[iFinD] 正在获取 {symbol} 的实时行情...\")\n            indicators = \"latest,pct_chg,change,volume,amount,high,low,open,preclose\"\n            df = realtime_quotes(symbol, indicators)\n            if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                row = df.iloc[0]\n                quotes = {\n                    \"symbol\": symbol,\n                    \"name\": row.get(\"name\", row.get(\"股票简称\")),\n                    \"price\": row.get(\"latest\"),\n                    \"change_percent\": row.get(\"pct_chg\"),\n                    \"change\": row.get(\"change\"),\n                    \"volume\": row.get(\"volume\"),\n                    \"amount\": row.get(\"amount\"),\n                    \"high\": row.get(\"high\"),\n                    \"low\": row.get(\"low\"),\n                    \"open\": row.get(\"open\"),\n                    \"pre_close\": row.get(\"preclose\"),\n                }\n                print(\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取实时行情\")\n                return quotes\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的实时行情（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n                df = self.tushare_api.daily(\n                    ts_code=ts_code,\n                    start_date=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\"),\n                    end_date=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\"),\n                )\n\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    row = df.iloc[0]\n                    quotes = {\n                        \"symbol\": symbol,\n                        \"price\": row[\"close\"],\n                        \"change_percent\": row[\"pct_chg\"],\n                        \"volume\": row[\"vol\"] * 100,\n                        \"amount\": row[\"amount\"] * 1000,\n                        \"high\": row[\"high\"],\n                        \"low\": row[\"low\"],\n                        \"open\": row[\"open\"],\n                        \"pre_close\": row[\"pre_close\"],\n                    }\n                    print(\"[Tushare] ✅ 成功获取实时行情\")\n                    return quotes\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        return quotes\n\n    def get_financial_data(self, symbol, report_type=\"income\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取财务数据（优先iFinD，失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码\n            report_type: 报表类型（'income'利润表, 'balance'资产负债表, 'cashflow'现金流量表）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 财务数据\n        \"\"\"\n        # 优先使用iFinD\n        try:\n            from ifind_client import wc\n\n            print(f\"[iFinD] 正在获取 {symbol} 的财务数据...\")\n            report_map = {\n                \"income\": \"利润表\",\n                \"balance\": \"资产负债表\",\n                \"cashflow\": \"现金流量表\",\n            }\n            report_label = report_map.get(report_type)\n            if report_label:\n                df = wc(f\"{symbol} {report_label}\")\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    print(\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取财务数据\")\n                    return df\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的财务数据（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n\n                if report_type == \"income\":\n                    df = self.tushare_api.income(ts_code=ts_code)\n                elif report_type == \"balance\":\n                    df = self.tushare_api.balancesheet(ts_code=ts_code)\n                elif report_type == \"cashflow\":\n                    df = self.tushare_api.cashflow(ts_code=ts_code)\n                else:\n                    df = None\n\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    print(\"[Tushare] ✅ 成功获取财务数据\")\n                    return df\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        return None\n\n    def _convert_to_ts_code(self, symbol):\n        \"\"\"\n        将6位股票代码转换为tushare格式（带市场后缀）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 6位股票代码\n\n        Returns:\n            str: tushare格式代码（如：000001.SZ）\n        \"\"\"\n        if not symbol or len(symbol) != 6:\n            return symbol\n\n        # 根据代码判断市场\n        if symbol.startswith(\"6\"):\n            # 上海主板\n            return f\"{symbol}.SH\"\n        elif symbol.startswith(\"0\") or symbol.startswith(\"3\"):\n            # 深圳主板和创业板\n            return f\"{symbol}.SZ\"\n        elif symbol.startswith(\"8\") or symbol.startswith(\"4\"):\n            # 北交所\n            return f\"{symbol}.BJ\"\n        else:\n            # 默认深圳\n            return f\"{symbol}.SZ\"\n\n    def _convert_from_ts_code(self, ts_code):\n        \"\"\"\n        将tushare格式代码转换为6位代码\n\n        Args:\n            ts_code: tushare格式代码（如：000001.SZ）\n\n        Returns:\n            str: 6位股票代码\n        \"\"\"\n        if \".\" in ts_code:\n            return ts_code.split(\".\")[0]\n        return ts_code\n\n\n# 全局数据源管理器实例\ndata_source_manager = DataSourceManager()"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":24,"aggregated":"\"流通市值\", info.get(\"circulating_market_cap\")\n                )\n                print(\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取基本信息\")\n                return info\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的基本信息（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n                df = self.tushare_api.stock_basic(\n                    ts_code=ts_code,\n                    fields=\"ts_code,name,area,industry,market,list_date\",\n                )\n\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    info[\"name\"] = df.iloc[0][\"name\"]\n                    info[\"industry\"] = df.iloc[0][\"industry\"]\n                    info[\"market\"] = df.iloc[0][\"market\"]\n                    info[\"list_date\"] = df.iloc[0][\"list_date\"]\n\n                    print(\"[Tushare] ✅ 成功获取基本信息\")\n                    return info\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        return info\n\n    def get_realtime_quotes(self, symbol):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取实时行情数据（优先iFinD，失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码\n\n        Returns:\n            dict: 实时行情数据\n        \"\"\"\n        quotes = {}\n\n        # 优先使用iFinD\n        try:\n            from ifind_client import realtime_quotes\n\n            print(f\"[iFinD] 正在获取 {symbol} 的实时行情...\")\n            indicators = \"latest,pct_chg,change,volume,amount,high,low,open,preclose\"\n            df = realtime_quotes(symbol, indicators)\n            if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                row = df.iloc[0]\n                quotes = {\n                    \"symbol\": symbol,\n                    \"name\": row.get(\"name\", row.get(\"股票简称\")),\n                    \"price\": row.get(\"latest\"),\n                    \"change_percent\": row.get(\"pct_chg\"),\n                    \"change\": row.get(\"change\"),\n                    \"volume\": row.get(\"volume\"),\n                    \"amount\": row.get(\"amount\"),\n                    \"high\": row.get(\"high\"),\n                    \"low\": row.get(\"low\"),\n                    \"open\": row.get(\"open\"),\n                    \"pre_close\": row.get(\"preclose\"),\n                }\n                print(\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取实时行情\")\n                return quotes\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的实时行情（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n                df = self.tushare_api.daily(\n                    ts_code=ts_code,\n                    start_date=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\"),\n                    end_date=datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\"),\n                )\n\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    row = df.iloc[0]\n                    quotes = {\n                        \"symbol\": symbol,\n                        \"price\": row[\"close\"],\n                        \"change_percent\": row[\"pct_chg\"],\n                        \"volume\": row[\"vol\"] * 100,\n                        \"amount\": row[\"amount\"] * 1000,\n                        \"high\": row[\"high\"],\n                        \"low\": row[\"low\"],\n                        \"open\": row[\"open\"],\n                        \"pre_close\": row[\"pre_close\"],\n                    }\n                    print(\"[Tushare] ✅ 成功获取实时行情\")\n                    return quotes\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        return quotes\n\n    def get_financial_data(self, symbol, report_type=\"income\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取财务数据（优先iFinD，失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码\n            report_type: 报表类型（'income'利润表, 'balance'资产负债表, 'cashflow'现金流量表）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 财务数据\n        \"\"\"\n        # 优先使用iFinD\n        try:\n            from ifind_client import wc\n\n            print(f\"[iFinD] 正在获取 {symbol} 的财务数据...\")\n            report_map = {\n                \"income\": \"利润表\",\n                \"balance\": \"资产负债表\",\n                \"cashflow\": \"现金流量表\",\n            }\n            report_label = report_map.get(report_type)\n            if report_label:\n                df = wc(f\"{symbol} {report_label}\")\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    print(\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取财务数据\")\n                    return df\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的财务数据（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n\n                if report_type == \"income\":\n                    df = self.tushare_api.income(ts_code=ts_code)\n                elif report_type == \"balance\":\n                    df = self.tushare_api.balancesheet(ts_code=ts_code)\n                elif report_type == \"cashflow\":\n                    df = self.tushare_api.cashflow(ts_code=ts_code)\n                else:\n                    df = None\n\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    print(\"[Tushare] ✅ 成功获取财务数据\")\n                    return df\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        return None\n\n    def _convert_to_ts_code(self, symbol):\n        \"\"\"\n        将6位股票代码转换为tushare格式（带市场后缀）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 6位股票代码\n\n        Returns:\n            str: tushare格式代码（如：000001.SZ）\n        \"\"\"\n        if not symbol or len(symbol) != 6:\n            return symbol\n\n        # 根据代码判断市场\n        if symbol.startswith(\"6\"):\n            # 上海主板\n            return f\"{symbol}.SH\"\n        elif symbol.startswith(\"0\") or symbol.startswith(\"3\"):\n            # 深圳主板和创业板\n            return f\"{symbol}.SZ\"\n        elif symbol.startswith(\"8\") or symbol.startswith(\"4\"):\n            # 北交所\n            return f\"{symbol}.BJ\"\n        else:\n            # 默认深圳\n            return f\"{symbol}.SZ\"\n\n    def _convert_from_ts_code(self, ts_code):\n        \"\"\"\n        将tushare格式代码转换为6位代码\n\n        Args:\n            ts_code: tushare格式代码（如：000001.SZ）\n\n        Returns:\n            str: 6位股票代码\n        \"\"\"\n        if \".\" in ts_code:\n            return ts_code.split(\".\")[0]\n        return ts_code\n\n\n# 全局数据源管理器实例\ndata_source_manager = DataSourceManager()","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776046930085}}
{"type":"message","id":"0a723e9c","parentId":"141cb968","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:22:28.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the architecture. The `DataSourceManager` class manages data sources for:\n1. `get_stock_hist_data` - historical data (iFinD primary, Tushare fallback)\n2. `get_realtime_quotes` - realtime quotes (iFinD primary, Tushare fallback)\n3. `get_financial_data` - financial data\n4. `get_basic_info` - basic info\n\nIt currently uses iFinD as primary and Tushare as fallback.\n\nI need to add gotdx as a new data source. But looking at the code more carefully, iFinD requires a proprietary license that costs money. \n\nSo in this user's case, only Tushare is available. The gotdx HTTP API would be a great real-time data source, but the AI-RXC's data_source_manager.py uses tushare which pulls historical data through its own API - it doesn't serve as a proxy to gotdx. I'd need to either modify the DataSourceManager to use gotdx for real-time quotes while keeping tushare for historical data, or create a new module entirely.\n\nLooking at the gotdx API documentation, `stock_quotes` already provides real-time market data including price, pre_close, change, volume, amount, and turnover. For real-time quotes specifically, gotdx would be much faster and more reliable than tushare. The app also has a smart_monitor_tdx_data.py module that queries a TDX API server via HTTP, which suggests there's already a pattern for making HTTP requests to a TDX server - I could follow that same approach with gotdx running on port 8089.\n\nThe most practical approach would be modifying the DataSourceManager to use gotdx for real-time quotes as the primary source with tushare as a fallback, while keeping tushare for historical data since gotdx doesn't seem designed for that. I should also check the config.py file to see if gotdx needs to be registered as a new data source option there.","thinkingSignature":"11cd1c630d5ca5345