{"type":"message","id":"b33f3cb0","parentId":"0a723e9c","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:22:28.460Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_m2z65o3nvqzk_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import os\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\n# 加载环境变量（override=True 强制覆盖已存在的环境变量）\nload_dotenv(override=True)\n\n# DeepSeek API配置\nDEEPSEEK_API_KEY = os.getenv(\"DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\", \"\")\nDEEPSEEK_BASE_URL = os.getenv(\"DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL\", \"https://api.deepseek.com\")\n\n# 其他配置\nTUSHARE_TOKEN = os.getenv(\"TUSHARE_TOKEN\", \"\")\n\n# 股票数据源配置\nDEFAULT_PERIOD = \"1y\"  # 默认获取1年数据\nDEFAULT_INTERVAL = \"1d\"  # 默认日线数据\n\n# MiniQMT量化交易配置\nMINIQMT_CONFIG = {\n    'enabled': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_ENABLED\", \"false\").lower() == \"true\",\n    'account_id': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_ACCOUNT_ID\", \"\"),\n    'host': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_HOST\", \"127.0.0.1\"),\n    'port': int(os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_PORT\", \"58610\")),\n}\n\n# TDX股票数据API配置项目地址github.com/oficcejo/tdx-api\nTDX_CONFIG = {\n    'enabled': os.getenv(\"TDX_ENABLED\", \"false\").lower() == \"true\",\n    'base_url': os.getenv(\"TDX_BASE_URL\", \"http://192.168.1.222:8181\"),\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":35,"aggregated":"import os\nfrom dotenv import load_dotenv\n\n# 加载环境变量（override=True 强制覆盖已存在的环境变量）\nload_dotenv(override=True)\n\n# DeepSeek API配置\nDEEPSEEK_API_KEY = os.getenv(\"DEEPSEEK_API_KEY\", \"\")\nDEEPSEEK_BASE_URL = os.getenv(\"DEEPSEEK_BASE_URL\", \"https://api.deepseek.com\")\n\n# 其他配置\nTUSHARE_TOKEN = os.getenv(\"TUSHARE_TOKEN\", \"\")\n\n# 股票数据源配置\nDEFAULT_PERIOD = \"1y\"  # 默认获取1年数据\nDEFAULT_INTERVAL = \"1d\"  # 默认日线数据\n\n# MiniQMT量化交易配置\nMINIQMT_CONFIG = {\n    'enabled': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_ENABLED\", \"false\").lower() == \"true\",\n    'account_id': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_ACCOUNT_ID\", \"\"),\n    'host': os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_HOST\", \"127.0.0.1\"),\n    'port': int(os.getenv(\"MINIQMT_PORT\", \"58610\")),\n}\n\n# TDX股票数据API配置项目地址github.com/oficcejo/tdx-api\nTDX_CONFIG = {\n    'enabled': os.getenv(\"TDX_ENABLED\", \"false\").lower() == \"true\",\n    'base_url': os.getenv(\"TDX_BASE_URL\", \"http://192.168.1.222:8181\"),\n}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776046948450}}
{"type":"message","id":"49911098","parentId":"b33f3cb0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:22:40.541Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see that there's already a `TDX_CONFIG` section for a TDX API. But that's a different TDX API (oficcejo/tdx-api), not gotdx.\n\nLet me look at how `smart_monitor_tdx_data.py` uses the TDX API, and then I can create a similar gotdx integration.\n\nActually, let me first check what the docker container can access. The gotdx is running on the Mac mini's port 8089. Docker containers can access the host via `host.docker.internal`. So I need to:\n\n1. Add a GOTDX config in `.env` \n2. Create a `gotdx_client.py` module\n\n\n3. Modify `data_source_manager.py` to use gotdx for realtime data\n\nThe Docker container for AI-RXC already exposes port 8503 to the host, so I can configure it to use `host.docker.internal:8089` for accessing the gotdx API running on the Mac mini. Let me check if the docker-compose.yml has a `network_mode` setting that might affect this connectivity.\n\nThe container runs on a custom bridge network without special host access, but since gotdx binds to `127.0.0.1:8089`, I need to verify whether `host.docker.internal` is properly routed through the bridge network. Looking at the Docker configuration, this should work by default on Docker Desktop for Mac, so I'll proceed with implementing the gotdx integration and testing connectivity from within the container.","thinkingSignature":"8dd234d669a96756e1ecc6d60e1baa28962f7554647be52dd89adf21f91e8d52"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vihmpik52yna_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/AI-RXC/docker-compose.yml","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":107318,"output":346,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":142870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776046948461,"responseId":"062b8