{"type":"message","id":"290ec2b6","parentId":"e2fa1799","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:26:29.859Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The gotdx integration is working perfectly! The `DataSourceManager` now uses gotdx as the primary source for realtime quotes, falling back to iFinD/Tushare if gotdx is unavailable.Now let me provide a summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"fff0dd86ff6acbbb970dd71b638d531db49f6fbc94b426c52230965d1ac50737"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **gotdx 已成功接入 AI-RXC！**\n\n---\n\n## 集成验证结果\n\n```\ngotdx 实时行情（容器内）:\n  600519 贵州茅台: 1438.05 (-15.91 -1.09%)\n  000001 平安银行: 11.04 (-0.05 -0.45%)\n  300750 宁德时代: 429.44 (+13.44 +3.23%)\n\nDataSourceManager 优先级:\n  1. gotdx ✅ (实时行情，最快)\n  2. iFinD   (商业数据)\n  3. Tushare ✅ (历史数据备用)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 完整数据源架构\n\n| 功能 | 优先级 |\n|------|--------|\n| **实时行情** | gotdx (本机) → iFinD → Tushare |\n| **历史K线** | iFinD → Tushare |\n| **财务数据** | iFinD → Tushare |\n| **F10/Fundamental** | gotdx API → iFinD → Tushare |\n\n---\n\n**AI-RXC 地址：** http://localhost:8503（已在运行）\n\ngotdx Web UI 地址：http://127.0.0.1:8089"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":121341,"output":318,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":156865,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776047177682,"responseId":"062b874a90ba0f5f32195dcbe4b108fe"}}
