{"type":"message","id":"e9ec0274","parentId":"1c9628a4","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:29:35.177Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 10:29:32 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b52f11e48a490c4952556ec52408]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52f11e48a490c4952556ec52408\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 10:29 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n想一下怎么把这些零散的仓库和功能整合起来"}],"timestamp":1776047375170}}
{"type":"message","id":"e41824cb","parentId":"e9ec0274","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:30:09.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to think about how to integrate all these scattered repositories and functionalities. Let me think about what's currently deployed and how they could work together.\n\nCurrent state:\n1. **AI-RXC** (Docker, ~/AI-RXC) - Stock analysis multi-agent system\n2. **gotdx** (host:8089) - TDX protocol HTTP API for real-time quotes\n3. **thsdata** (host Python) - THS real-time data (native macOS)\n4. **oMLX** (host:8000) - Local LLM inference server\n5. **OpenClaw** - The agent system itself\n\nIntegration possibilities:\n\n\n- AI-RXC already uses gotdx via `host.docker.internal:8089` for real-time quotes\n- oMLX could potentially serve as a local LLM backend for AI-RXC instead of relying on DeepSeek's cloud API\n- thsdata on the host could feed into gotdx or serve as a backup data source\n- OpenClaw could orchestrate workflows across these systems\n\nThe core opportunity is making oMLX handle inference locally while AI-RXC focuses on stock analysis, gotdx provides market data, and OpenClaw ties everything together as the coordination layer.\n\nI should think through a practical architecture for how these components actually communicate and what the data flow looks like.","thinkingSignature":"b87072c79a959c84da0e65b3cad2c6c9cf0f7b660e871c863a6e71356fab5566"},{"type":"text","text":"这是个值得想清楚的问题。让我梳理一下现状，再给整合方案。\n\n---\n\n## 现状盘点\n\n| 组件 | 位置 | 状态 | 核心能力 |\n|------|------|------|----------|\n| **AI-RXC** | Docker | ✅ 运行中 | 多Agent股票分析、主力资金跟踪 |\n| **gotdx** | 主机 8089 | ✅ 运行中 | A股实时行情（HTTP API）|\n| **thsdata** | 主机 Python | ✅ 已安装 | 同花顺实时行情（原生） |\n| **oMLX** | 主机 8000 | ✅ 运行中 | 本地LLM推理（OmniCoder等） |\n| **OpenClaw** | 主机 | ✅ 运行中 | 整体编排、飞书通知 |\n\n---\n\n## 整合思路\n\n**数据流：**\n```\ngotdx (HTTP)  ──→  AI-RXC 实时行情\n                        │\n                 oMLX 本地推理  ←── DeepSeek API（云端）\n                        │\n                     结论/报告\n                        │\n                  飞书通知（OpenClaw）\n```\n\n**最实际的整合方向：**\n\n### ① oMLX → AI-RXC（本地推理层）\nAI-RXC 目前用 DeepSeek 云端 API。可以改造成：\n- **轻度任务**（选股筛选、技术指标）：oMLX + OmniCoder\n- **重度任务**（主力资金分析、复合判断）：DeepSeek 云端\n\n### ② thsdata → gotdx 互备\n- gotdx 用 **TDX 协议**（主行情服务器）\n- thsdata 用 **THS 协议**（同花顺直连）\n- 两者协议不同、服务器不同，可以互补\n\n### ③ 统一到 OpenClaw 调度\n所有定时任务（每日简报、盘后复盘）由 OpenClaw cron 触发，调用不同服务。\n\n---\n\n## 瓶颈 & 建议\n\n| 问题 | 现状 | 建议 |\n|------|------|------|\n| gotdx 没有**历史K线** | 仅有实时 | 用 Tushare 补充 |\n| AI-RXC 与 OpenClaw **未打通** | 独立运行 | 通过 HTTP 调用 |\n| thsdata 游客账户**不稳定** | 临时方案 | 建议用自己的 THS 账号 |\n\n---\n\n**现在最值得做的一件事：** 让 AI-RXC 的数据源优先级固化——实时行情走 gotdx，历史/K线走 Tushare，thsdata 作为降级备选。\n\n你觉得这个方向对吗？还是有别的整合优先级？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":822,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":129721,"totalTokens":165882,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776047375188,"responseId":"062b880f1e04033352a1cf0869dc2b90"}}
