{"type":"message","id":"c8693f65","parentId":"80aa0166","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:31:07.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user confirmed the direction is correct. Now I should ask for clarification on what to prioritize - or just proceed with the most practical next step.\n\nGiven the \"simple first, 给标准不给步骤\" principle I just added, I should ask which one to do first rather than assume.\n\nActually, looking at what I just said:\n> **现在最值得做的一件事：** 让 AI-RXC 的数据源优先级固化——实时行情走 gotdx，历史/K线走 Tushare，thsdata 作为降级备选。\n\nThis is already partially done - I integrated gotdx into AI-RXC's data_source_manager with priority. But the data source priority is for `get_realtime_quotes` only. \n\nI'm realizing `get_stock_hist_data` still relies on iFinD and Tushare without gotdx for historical data. So my next step should be consolidating the data source priority for historical K-lines - setting gotdx as primary for real-time, Tushare as primary for historical data, with thsdata as fallback.","thinkingSignature":"a7be20554b5472071060637c1417e19fcbc712b95b1c86070156f71bd881dbd8"},{"type":"text","text":"那这一件事我来做：\n\n**AI-RXC 数据源优先级固化（历史K线方向）：**\n\n当前 `get_stock_hist_data` 还是 iFinD → Tushare，没有利用 gotdx。让我把它也加上 gotdx 支持，然后明确各数据源的职责边界。\n\n```\n实时行情：gotdx → thsdata → Tushare\n历史K线：gotdx → Tushare → thsdata\n```\n\n等等——gotdx 的 `/api/kline` 接口支持日K/周K/月K，可以替代部分 Tushare 的历史数据需求。先让我看看 gotdx 的 K线能力，再统一改造。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":342,"cacheRead":165080,"cacheWrite":651,"totalTokens":166206,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776047443028,"responseId":"062b88536e08d325b9b5858ccf69f210"}}
