{"type":"message","id":"075533ed","parentId":"376c4b4a","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:32:34.690Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 10:32:33 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b52f112cb40b8c3c14f8b58aeebe, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52f112cb40b8c3c14f8b58aeebe\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 10:32 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n**豆包给你的微小补强建议（不破坏现有设计）**\n1. **给行情源加健康检查**\nOpenClaw 定时 ping gotdx /thsdata，自动切源，不用手动改配置。\n2. **AI-RXC 增加推理路由配置文件**\n哪些任务走本地 oMLX，哪些走 DeepSeek，写在 config 里，不要硬编码。\n3. **历史 K 线统一归一化**\ngotdx、Tushare、ths 数据格式不同，AI-RXC 内部加一层适配器，保证 AI 看到的结构一致。\n4. **oMLX 本地推理加缓存**\n同样股票、同样日期的简单分析，直接读缓存，减少重复计算。"}],"timestamp":1776047554683}}
{"type":"message","id":"f05a3f7c","parentId":"075533ed","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:32:58.570Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user shared advice from Doubao (another AI) about strengthening the existing design. These are good suggestions. Let me evaluate them:\n\n1. **Health check for data sources** - OpenClaw pings gotdx/thsdata periodically and auto-switches. This is a good idea.\n\n2. **AI-RXC inference routing config** - which tasks go to oMLX (local) vs DeepSeek (cloud), configurable not hardcoded.\n\n3. **Historical K-line normalization** - different formats from gotdx, Tushare, ths, add an adapter layer so AI sees consistent structure.\n\n4. **oMLX local inference caching** - same stock + same date analysis → cache, reduce duplicate computation.\n \nThese are solid architectural improvements. I should prioritize them by impact: the data format adapter (3) would have the widest benefit across the system, followed by the health check routing (1), then the inference routing config (2), and finally caching (4). I'll work through these in that order.\n\nActually, I need to reconsider the approach. The existing `data_source_manager.py` already handles gotdx, Tushare, and iFinD fallbacks for real-time quotes, but it's missing gotdx K-line support. So the immediate priority should be adding gotdx K-line capabilities, then tackling the broader architecture improvements like the adapter layer, health checks, and inference routing.\n\nBut wait—the user's original request was specifically about solidifying the data source priority. I should clarify whether they want me to start implementing these suggestions now or if they prefer to discuss the approach first. Let me ask before diving in.\n\nActually, thinking about this more practically: since gotdx supports K-line queries and we already have a client module, the most straightforward next step is adding K-line support to `data_source_manager`. That's the foundation everything else builds on. Once that's in place, the other architectural improvements become much clearer to design and implement.\n\nSo I should respond by acknowledging these are good suggestions, then propose a concrete plan starting with adding K-line capability to the existing data source manager, followed by proposing priorities for the rest.","thinkingSignature":"257fe704f80dcd8a7741c1471c48b51c89aec0e497f5bab8ed7ee7f72bbfafbc"},{"type":"text","text":"豆包的建议都很到位。让我先做好最底层的一件事——**把 gotdx K线加进 `data_source_manager.py`**，这是后面所有架构的基础。\n\n然后我给你一个**整合路线图**，排优先级，你选哪件先做。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ebg1hsjreuak_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/AI-RXC/data_source_manager.py","offset":36,"limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":541,"cacheRead":165754,"cacheWrite":514,"totalTokens":166942,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776047554701,"responseId":"062b88c3176f296b7b04d599121f1068"}}
