{"type":"message","id":"9cd74f7e","parentId":"37fa1bb0","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:33:24.148Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_om6c1zw5tfcx_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        else:\n            print(\"ℹ️ 未配置Tushare Token\")\n\n    def get_stock_hist_data(self, symbol, start_date=None, end_date=None, adjust=\"qfq\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取股票历史数据（优先iFinD，失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码（6位数字）\n            start_date: 开始日期（格式：'20240101'或'2024-01-01'）\n            end_date: 结束日期\n            adjust: 复权类型（'qfq'前复权, 'hfq'后复权, ''不复权）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 包含日期、开盘、收盘、最高、最低、成交量等列\n        \"\"\"\n        # 标准化日期格式\n        if start_date:\n            start_date = start_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        if end_date:\n            end_date = end_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        else:\n            end_date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n        # 优先使用iFinD\n        try:\n            from ifind_client import history_quotes\n\n            print(f\"[iFinD] 正在获取 {symbol} 的历史数据...\")\n            indicators = \"open,high,low,close,volume,amount,pct_chg,turnover\"\n            df = history_quotes(\n                symbol, indicators, start_date, end_date, params=f\"adj={adjust}\"\n            )\n\n            if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                df = df.rename(\n                    columns={\n                        \"time\": \"date\",\n                        \"date\": \"date\",\n                        \"pct_chg\": \"pct_change\",\n                    }\n                )\n                if \"date\" in df.columns:\n                    df[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df[\"date\"])\n                print(f\"[iFinD] ✅ 成功获取 {len(df)} 条数据\")\n                return df\n        except Exception as e:\n            print(f\"[iFinD] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # iFinD失败，尝试tushare\n        if self.tushare_available:\n            try:\n                print(f\"[Tushare] 正在获取 {symbol} 的历史数据（备用数据源）...\")\n\n                # 转换股票代码格式（添加市场后缀）\n                ts_code = self._convert_to_ts_code(symbol)\n\n                # 转换复权类型\n                adj_dict = {\"qfq\": \"qfq\", \"hfq\": \"hfq\", \"\": None}\n                adj = adj_dict.get(adjust, \"qfq\")\n\n                # 格式化日期\n                start = (\n                    f\"{start_date[:4]}-{start_date[4:6]}-{start_date[6:]}\"\n                    if start_date\n                    else None\n                )\n                end = (\n                    f\"{end_date[:4]}-{end_date[4:6]}-{end_date[6:]}\"\n                    if end_date\n                    else None\n                )\n\n                # 获取数据\n                df = self.tushare_api.daily(\n                    ts_code=ts_code, start_date=start_date, end_date=end_date, adj=adj\n                )\n\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    # 标准化列名和数据格式\n\n[282 more lines in file. Use offset=125 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776047604141}}
{"type":"message","id":"4d76c720","parentId":"9cd74f7e","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:33:44.211Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add gotdx K-line support to `get_stock_hist_data`. The gotdx `get_kline` method already supports category (K线类型) and adjust (复权). Let me modify `get_stock_hist_data` to use gotdx first, then fall back to iFinD, then Tushare.\n\nThe gotdx `get_kline` method has these parameters:\n- `category`: 0=5分钟, 1=15分钟, 2=30分钟, 3=1小时, 4=日K, 5=周K, 6=月K, 7=1分钟, 8=季K, 9=年K\n\n\n- `adjust`: 0=不复权, 1=前复权, 2=后复权\n\nI'll modify the method to insert gotdx as the first option for daily/weekly/monthly K-line data (categories 4, 5, 6), then keep iFinD → Tushare as fallbacks.","thinkingSignature":"f48e59f3601c80b95aa73cf14934eab28b6ce90ba8833f74759968cc0dc1595b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_z9ceuh4hezor_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/AI-RXC/data_source_manager.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    def get_stock_hist_data(self, symbol, start_date=None, end_date=None, adjust=\"qfq\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取股票历史数据（优先iFinD，失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码（6位数字）\n            start_date: 开始日期（格式：'20240101'或'2024-01-01'）\n            end_date: 结束日期\n            adjust: 复权类型（'qfq'前复权, 'hfq'后复权, ''不复权）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 包含日期、开盘、收盘、最高、最低、成交量等列\n        \"\"\"\n        # 标准化日期格式\n        if start_date:\n            start_date = start_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        if end_date:\n            end_date = end_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        else:\n            end_date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n        # 优先使用iFinD","newText":"    def get_stock_hist_data(self, symbol, start_date=None, end_date=None, adjust=\"qfq\"):\n        \"\"\"\n        获取股票历史数据（优先gotdx，iFinD失败时使用tushare）\n\n        Args:\n            symbol: 股票代码（6位数字）\n            start_date: 开始日期（格式：'20240101'或'2024-01-01'）\n            end_date: 结束日期\n            adjust: 复权类型（'qfq'前复权, 'hfq'后复权, ''不复权）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 包含日期、开盘、收盘、最高、最低、成交量等列\n        \"\"\"\n        # 标准化日期格式\n        if start_date:\n            start_date = start_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        if end_date:\n            end_date = end_date.replace(\"-\", \"\")\n        else:\n            end_date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n\n        # gotdx优先（日K/周K/月K支持前复权）\n        if self.gotdx_client:\n            try:\n                adj_map = {\"qfq\": 1, \"hfq\": 2, \"\": 0}\n                adj_val = adj_map.get(adjust, 1)\n                df = self.gotdx_client.get_kline(symbol, category=4, count=300, adjust=adj_val)\n                if df is not None and not df.empty:\n                    df = df[(df[\"date\"] >= start_date) & (df[\"date\"] <= end_date)]\n                    if not df.empty:\n                        print(f\"[gotdx] ✅ 成功获取 {symbol} {len(df)} 条历史K线\")\n                        return df\n            except Exception as e:\n                print(f\"[gotdx] ❌ 获取失败: {e}\")\n\n        # gotdx失败，使用iFinD"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133329,"output":969,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":169504,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776047604150,"responseId":"062b88f4f1815487bf0faa5629b532bb"}}
