x API running, 74 methods available\n- Assistant: ✅ **gotdx 部署完成！**\n\n---\n\n## gotdx WebViewer\n\n| 项目 | 值 |\n|------|------|\n| **访问地址** | http://127.0.0.1:8089 |\n| **API 方法数** | 74 个 |\n| **状态** | 运行中（开机自启脚本已备好）|\n\n---\n\n## 功能概览\n\n**股票行情**（主站）：批量行情、K线、分时、逐笔成交、集合竞价、历史成交\n**指数/监控**：指数概况、异动监控、成交分布、排行九宫格\n**F10资料**：公司信息、财务数据、除权除息、板块文件\n**扩展市场**：港股、美股等（MAC协议）\n**测速**：主站/扩展站/MAC 节点延迟测速\n\n---\n\n## 下一步\n\n这个 gotdx API 是 HTTP 接口，**Docker 内的 AI-RXC 可以直接调用**（通过 `http://host.docker.internal:8089`），比 TUSHARE 更稳定、更快。\n\n要我把这个 gotdx API 接入 AI-RXC 的数据源配置吗？\n[non-text content: thinking]\n\n<read-files>\n/Users/ling/AI-RXC/data_source_manager.py\n\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/AI-RXC/.env\n/Users/ling/AI-RXC/.env\n/Users/ling/AI-RXC/docker-compose.yml\n/Users/ling/AI-RXC/gotdx_client.py\n/Users/ling/Library/LaunchAgents/com.gotdx.webviewer.plist\n/tmp/download_ai_rxc.py\n\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"0bb9d28a","tokensBefore":173669,"details":{"readFiles":["/Users/ling/AI-RXC/data_source_manager.py"],"modifiedFiles":["/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/AI-RXC/.env","/Users/ling/AI-RXC/.env","/Users/ling/AI-RXC/docker-compose.yml","/Users/ling/AI-RXC/gotdx_client.py","/Users/ling/Library/LaunchAgents/com.gotdx.webviewer.plist","/tmp/download_ai_rxc.py"]},"fromHook":true}
{"type":"message","id":"daca6883","parentId":"aa5ca247","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:36:42.889Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-13 10:32:33 GMT+8] Feishu[coding-agent] DM | 张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae) [msg:om_x100b52f112cb40b8c3c14f8b58aeebe, post]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b52f112cb40b8c3c14f8b58aeebe\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-04-13 10:32 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\n**豆包给你的微小补强建议（不破坏现有设计）**\n1. **给行情源加健康检查**\nOpenClaw 定时 ping gotdx /thsdata，自动切源，不用手动改配置。\n2. **AI-RXC 增加推理路由配置文件**\n哪些任务走本地 oMLX，哪些走 DeepSeek，写在 config 里，不要硬编码。\n3. **历史 K 线统一归一化**\ngotdx、Tushare、ths 数据格式不同，AI-RXC 内部加一层适配器，保证 AI 看到的结构一致。\n4. **oMLX 本地推理加缓存**\n同样股票、同样日期的简单分析，直接读缓存，减少重复计算。"}],"timestamp":1776047802876}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ae0873d","parentId":"daca6883","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:36:55.577Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent the same Doubao suggestions again. I was already working on the gotdx kline integration. Let me continue fixing the gotdx kline API call and then address these suggestions in priority order.\n\nLooking at the gotdx source code, the stock_kline API returns columns: `[\"datetime\", \"open\", \"high\", \"low\", \"close\", \"vol\", \"amount\", \"turnover\"]`. The issue was that my call to gotdx kline failed with 400 Bad Request.\n\nLet me check the actual API format more carefully. Looking at the source code:\n- category: uint16\n- market: uint8\n- code: string\n\n\n- start: uint16\n- count: uint16\n- times: uint16\n- adjust: uint16\n\nThe gotdx client Python code might be passing these as strings instead of raw numbers, which could be causing the serialization mismatch. I need to trace through how the gotdx_client.py formats the request and compares it against what the Go API expects.","thinkingSignature":"c62691b1597f91bf5591a869eeaebae13d6fb6e689164c63d6d1e146d550e9cd"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，继续修 gotdx K线——接口格式对不上，先看看 `gotdx_client.py` 的实现。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s208pjd27x9i_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/AI-RXC/gotdx_client.py","offset":140,"limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":133,"output":290,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":30031,"totalTokens":65660,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776047802911,"responseId":"062b89bbf264332bba179b48bd42ee76"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c8d71d2d","parentId":"8ae0873d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:36:55.653Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_s208pjd27x9i_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"            \"market\": market,\n            \"code\": code,\n            \"start\": start,\n            \"count\": count,\n            \"times\": 1,\n            \"adjust\": adjust,\n        })\n\n        if not result or not result.get(\"rows\"):\n            return pd.DataFrame()\n\n        cols = result.get(\"columns\", [])\n        df = pd.DataFrame(result[\"rows\"], columns=cols)\n\n        # 标准化字段\n        df = df.rename(columns={\n            \"time\": \"date\",\n            \"vol\": \"volume\",\n        })\n\n        if \"date\" in df.columns:\n            df[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df[\"date\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n\n        for col in [\"open\", \"high\", \"low\", \"close\", \"volume\", \"amount\", \"turnover\"]:\n            if col in df.columns:\n                df[col] = pd.to_numeric(df[col], errors=\"coerce\")\n\n        return df\n\n    def get_call_auction(self, code: str, market: int = None) -> pd.DataFrame:\n        \"\"\"\n        获取集合竞价数据\n\n        Args:\n            code: 股票代码\n            market: 市场（0=深圳, 1=上海）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 包含 time, price, bid2_vol, ask2_vol, cur_volume\n        \"\"\"\n        if market is None:\n            market = 1 if code.startswith(\"6\") else 0\n\n        result = self._call(\"stock_auction\", {\n            \"market\": market,\n            \"code\": code,\n            \"start\": 0,\n            \"count\": 100,\n        })\n\n\n[49 more lines in file. Use offset=190 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776047815650}}
{"type":"message","id":"c016ddc9","parentId":"c8d71d2d","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:36:59.138Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me look at the get_kline method more specifically to see how it calls the API.","thinkingSignature":"3d8ae2e4ee502c097f600ab747ae53cf6d92f5d763d67692d03d9ea9bcd33125"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r6kxdaacjnis_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/AI-RXC/gotdx_client.py","offset":120,"limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30817,"output":77,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66100,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776047815654,"responseId":"062b89c74dfea931a16895da25532f03"}}
{"type":"message","id":"85128ea9","parentId":"c016ddc9","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:36:59.214Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_r6kxdaacjnis_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        \"\"\"\n        获取K线数据\n\n        Args:\n            code: 股票代码，如 \"000001\"\n            market: 市场（0=深圳, 1=上海），自动判断\n            category: K线类型（0=5分钟, 1=15分钟, 2=30分钟, 3=1小时,\n                               4=日K, 5=周K, 6=月K, 7=1分钟, 8=季K, 9=年K）\n            start: 起始位置\n            count: 数量\n            adjust: 复权（0=不复权, 1=前复权, 2=后复权）\n\n        Returns:\n            DataFrame: 包含 time, open, high, low, close, volume, amount, turnover\n        \"\"\"\n        if market is None:\n            market = 1 if code.startswith(\"6\") else 0\n\n        result = self._call(\"stock_kline\", {\n            \"category\": category,\n            \"market\": market,\n            \"code\": code,\n            \"start\": start,\n            \"count\": count,\n            \"times\": 1,\n            \"adjust\": adjust,\n        })\n\n        if not result or not result.get(\"rows\"):\n            return pd.DataFrame()\n\n        cols = result.get(\"columns\", [])\n        df = pd.DataFrame(result[\"rows\"], columns=cols)\n\n        # 标准化字段\n        df = df.rename(columns={\n            \"time\": \"date\",\n            \"vol\": \"volume\",\n        })\n\n        if \"date\" in df.columns:\n            df[\"date\"] = pd.to_datetime(df[\"date\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n\n        for col in [\"open\", \"high\", \"low\", \"close\", \"volume\", \"amount\", \"turnover\"]:\n            if col in df.columns:\n                df[col] = pd.to_numeric(df[col], errors=\"coerce\")\n\n        return df\n\n    def get_call_auction(self, code: str, market: int = None) -> pd.DataFrame:\n\n[69 more lines in file. Use offset=170 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776047819210}}
