{"type":"message","id":"4b96fe94","parentId":"d14dacef","timestamp":"2026-04-13T02:48:54.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Doubao page is rendering content dynamically with JavaScript, so I can't get the content with simple curl. Let me try with a more sophisticated approach using the xiaohongshu skill which handles dynamic content, or try to use playwright-based tools.\n\nActually, the user already shared the content in the earlier message! Looking back at the conversation:\n\n```\n**豆包给你的微小补强建议（不破坏现有设计）**\n1. **给行情源加健康检查**\nOpenClaw 定时 ping gotdx /thsdata，自动切源，不用手动改配置。","thinkingSignature":"984cbafb8943a92e4602b0254975c501fd57a4c670e0ffbf6d61bb45adca3c24"},{"type":"text","text":"页面是 JS 动态渲染的，直接抓不到。但你之前已经把豆包的建议贴过来了，我直接评：\n\n---\n\n## 豆包建议评估\n\n### ① 给行情源加健康检查\n**合理，而且紧迫。** 行情源随时可能断，当前是\"挂了才知道\"。OpenClaw 定时 ping → 自动切源，这个设计很标准。可以做。\n\n### ② AI-RXC 增加推理路由配置\n**方向对，但时机未到。** oMLX 还没正式接进来（本地模型在跑吗？），硬做路由配置是提前设计。等 oMLX 跑通再说。\n\n### ③ 历史K线统一归一化\n**合理，但已有部分基础。** `data_source_manager.py` 里的 `get_stock_hist_data` 已经在做格式归一化（`date`、`open`、`high` 等字段统一）。缺口是：不同数据源的字段名/类型差异（字符串 vs 数字、日期格式）还没完全消除。可以做，但优先级低。\n\n### ④ oMLX 本地推理加缓存\n**合理，但依赖②。** ②没做之前，缓存没有意义归属。\n\n---\n\n## 我的判断\n\n| 建议 | 合理？ | 现在做？ |\n|------|--------|----------|\n| ①健康检查 | ✅ | ✅ 先做 |\n| ②推理路由 | ✅ | ❌ 等oMLX |\n| ③归一化 | ✅ | ❌ 已有基础 |\n| ④缓存 | ✅ | ❌ 等② |\n\n**现在做 ①**，大概半小时搞定。要开始吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":49424,"output":449,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85079,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776048515468,"responseId":"062b8c84dd70d660e1ce6eb4b1dbb739"}}
