{"type":"message","id":"eadc1d94","parentId":"a12d7202","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:08:57.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The problem is that `model` is being passed both as a positional argument and also in `extra_cfg`. I need to fix the inference_router to not include model in extra_cfg if it's already being passed explicitly.\n\nAlso, I need to fix `gotdx` health check - it's returning False but gotdx is working. Let me look at the health check code.\n\nLooking at the health check: `results[\"gotdx\"] = df is not None and not df.empty` - this should work. But `gotdx` returned `False` even though realtime quotes work. The issue might be that the health check only checks 000001 which is平安银行, and maybe gotdx doesn't support that specific query in the health check... but wait, the actual realtime quotes test worked fine.\n \nOh, I see it now - there's a variable naming issue where the health check result dict uses `\"gotdx\"` but the realtime quotes code uses `self.is_healthy(\"gotdx\")` which checks the cached `_health_status`. The dict returned from `_run_health_checks()` is the fresh result, but the cached status might be stale or the keys don't match between the two places.\n\nThe omlx health check actually passed and returned `True` for gotdx, so the logic is working - the problem is just that duplicate `model` parameter being passed to the LLM call, and the gotdx result being False because of that caching mismatch.","thinkingSignature":"17b3d1fd0b4934d88b0ba5e12567910e29954e2f03cdf3aee4cb203962a69235"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c3jl5342x3u9_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/AI-RXC/services/inference_router.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    # 调用 LLM\n    extra_cfg = llm_cfg or {}\n    if model:\n        extra_cfg[\"model\"] = model\n\n    result = call_llm(\n        provider=provider,\n        model=model or (llm_cfg.get(\"model\") if llm_cfg else \"deepseek-chat\"),\n        messages=messages,\n        temperature=temperature,\n        max_tokens=max_tokens,\n        **(extra_cfg or {}),\n    )","newText":"    # 调用 LLM\n    extra_cfg = dict(llm_cfg) if llm_cfg else {}\n    extra_cfg.pop(\"model\", None)  # model单独传，避免重复\n    extra_cfg.pop(\"provider\", None)\n    extra_cfg.pop(\"messages\", None)\n    extra_cfg.pop(\"temperature\", None)\n    extra_cfg.pop(\"max_tokens\", None)\n\n    resolved_model = model or (llm_cfg.get(\"model\") if llm_cfg else None) or (\n        \"deepseek-chat\" if provider == \"deepseek\" else \"OmniCoder-9B-Instruct-4bit\"\n    )\n\n    result = call_llm(\n        provider=provider,\n        model=resolved_model,\n        messages=messages,\n        temperature=temperature,\n        max_tokens=max_tokens,\n        **extra_cfg,\n    )"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":76561,"output":653,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112420,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776049720590,"responseId":"062b9139aa04570e4d07070246e74bf3"}}
