{"type":"message","id":"34a85de7","parentId":"40019a08","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:15:32.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me run the full test.","thinkingSignature":"6ede01bf9138ae0a9d7ba995d4a5d7184d83070336d8d01c0b9eb63e781c3b04"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_06uvf63jv1v7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"docker exec agentsstock1 python3 -c \"\nimport sys, time\nsys.path.insert(0, '/app')\n\nprint('=== oMLX直连测试 ===')\nfrom services.llm_router import call_llm\nt0 = time.time()\nresult = call_llm(\n    provider='omlx',\n    model='OmniCoder-9B-Instruct-4bit',\n    messages=[{'role':'user','content':'判断：茅台涨跌是否超过2%？只答是或否。'}],\n    temperature=0.05,\n    max_tokens=100,\n    timeout_config={'total': 60},\n)\nprint(f'  ok: {result.get(\\\"ok\\\")}, dur: {time.time()-t0:.1f}s')\nif result.get('ok'):\n    print(f'  text: {result.get(\\\"text\\\",\\\"\\\")[:100]}')\nelse:\n    print(f'  err: {result.get(\\\"error_type\\\")} {result.get(\\\"error_message\\\",\\\"\\\")[:200]}')\n\nprint()\nprint('=== 推理路由（stock_screen → omlx，第1次冷调用）===')\nfrom services.inference_router import inference\nt0 = time.time()\nr = inference(task_type='stock_screen', stock_code='600519', date='20260413',\n    prompt='判断：茅台涨跌是否超过2%？只答是或否。', skip_cache=True)\nprint(f'  provider: {r.get(\\\"provider\\\")}, ok: {r.get(\\\"ok\\\")}, dur: {time.time()-t0:.1f}s')\nif r.get('ok'):\n    print(f'  text: {r.get(\\\"text\\\",\\\"\\\")[:100]}')\n    print(f'  cache_hit: {r.get(\\\"cache_hit\\\")}')\nelse:\n    print(f'  err: {r.get(\\\"error_type\\\")} {r.get(\\\"error_message\\\",\\\"\\\")[:200]}')\n\nprint()\nprint('=== 推理路由（第2次，应该命中缓存）===')\nt0 = time.time()\nr2 = inference(task_type='stock_screen', stock_code='600519', date='20260413',\n    prompt='判断：茅台涨跌是否超过2%？只答是或否。', skip_cache=False)\nprint(f'  provider: {r2.get(\\\"provider\\\")}, ok: {r2.get(\\\"ok\\\")}, dur: {time.time()-t0:.1f}s')\nprint(f'  cache_hit: {r2.get(\\\"cache_hit\\\")}')\n\" 2>&1 | grep -v \"INFO\\|WARNING\\|account\\|mac\\|失效\\|建议\\|配置\\|临时\\|游客\\|旅客\\|THS\\|✅ TCP\\|断开\\|连接\"","timeout":120}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":89876,"output":625,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125707,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776050119807,"responseId":"062b92c8634f390a166415eb38ef9211"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2094d776","parentId":"34a85de7","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:15:39.495Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_06uvf63jv1v7_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"=== oMLX直连测试 ===\n  ok: True, dur: 6.2s\n  text: Thinking Process:\n\n1.  **Analyze the Request:**\n    *   User: \"判断：茅台涨跌是否超过 2%？只答是或否。\" (Judge: Did Mo\n\n=== 推理路由（stock_screen → omlx，第1次冷调用）===\n[inference_router] omlx 不健康，自动降级到 deepseek\n  provider: deepseek, ok: False, dur: 0.4s\n  err: provider Client error '400 Bad Request' for url 'https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions'\nFor more information check: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/400\n\n=== 推理路由（第2次，应该命中缓存）===\n[inference_router] omlx 不健康，自动降级到 deepseek\n  provider: deepseek, ok: False, dur: 0.1s\n  cache_hit: False"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":7096,"aggregated":"=== oMLX直连测试 ===\n  ok: True, dur: 6.2s\n  text: Thinking Process:\n\n1.  **Analyze the Request:**\n    *   User: \"判断：茅台涨跌是否超过 2%？只答是或否。\" (Judge: Did Mo\n\n=== 推理路由（stock_screen → omlx，第1次冷调用）===\n[inference_router] omlx 不健康，自动降级到 deepseek\n  provider: deepseek, ok: False, dur: 0.4s\n  err: provider Client error '400 Bad Request' for url 'https://api.deepseek.com/v1/chat/completions'\nFor more information check: https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Status/400\n\n=== 推理路由（第2次，应该命中缓存）===\n[inference_router] omlx 不健康，自动降级到 deepseek\n  provider: deepseek, ok: False, dur: 0.1s\n  cache_hit: False","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776050139479}}
{"type":"message","id":"c62843f8","parentId":"2094d776","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:16:23.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Two issues:\n1. oMLX direct call works fine (6.2s)\n2. The health check still says omlx is unhealthy → it falls back to deepseek\n3. But deepseek returns 400 Bad Request\n\nThe health check issue: `is_healthy(\"omlx\")` in `inference_router.py` is using its own health check logic, which might be different from what works for the direct call. Let me debug the health check in `inference_router.py`.\n\nLooking at `inference_router.py`'s `check_provider_health`:```python\nif provider == \"omlx\":\n    import httpx\n    omlx_cfg = config.get(\"omlx\", {})\n\n\n```\n\nI'm extracting the omlx configuration with the base URL and API key, then stripping any trailing `/v1` from the base URL before making a request to the models endpoint with the authorization header. The issue is likely in how I'm constructing the URL or handling the response from that endpoint.\n\nThe health check worked for `run_health_checks()` which returned `{'gotdx': False, 'omlx': True}`, but then when `inference()` checks `get_health_status(\"omlx\")`, it's returning `False` even though the stored status shows `True`. I think the problem is a stale cache—`get_health_status()` might be returning an outdated value from an earlier health check that hadn't properly updated the internal `_health_status` dictionary yet. I'm realizing the issue might be in how `inference_router.py` initializes its module-level `_health_status` dictionary at import time—it could be creating a reference that gets replaced rather than updated when `_run_health_checks()` reassigns the dict, so the inference function is still reading from the old empty dict. I'm realizing the issue might be with how `_health_lock` is initialized at the module level versus as an instance variable—maybe there's a scoping problem where the lock being used in `get_health_status` isn't the same one protecting `_health_status` when it gets checked. I'm realizing the issue might be in how `run_health_checks()` is being called before `inference()` gets invoked. Looking at the health check results showing `{'gotdx': False, 'omlx': True}`, then `inference()` immediately says \"omlx 不健康\" - this suggests the health status might be getting overwritten between when the checks run and when `inference()` reads them. The `_health_status` variable in `inference_router.py` is module-level and initialized empty, so maybe it's being reset somewhere after the initial health checks pass but before the inference call. I'm checking the `is_healthy` logic more carefully—when `status` is a boolean False, the condition should trigger and return True, causing a fallback. But when it's a boolean True, the condition should be False and no fallback should occur. The message \"omlx 不健康\" means the fallback triggered, so `status` must be evaluating as falsy at that moment. Looking at the timing, `run_health_checks()` returns `{'gotdx': False, 'omlx': True}`, and then `inference()` is called, which invokes `get_health_status(\"omlx\")` and gets the boolean value from the status dictionary. True}. But then in `inference`, it prints \"omlx 不健康\"... unless the message is printed in a different call.\n\nActually wait - looking at the test output more carefully: the \"omlx 不健康\" message appears on the inference call, not on the health_checks call. The health check says `{'gotdx': False, 'omlx': True}`. Then inference says \"omlx 不健康\".\n\nThis is bizarre unless there's a race condition where the module-level `_health_status` gets reset somehow.\n\nActually, I just realized something important. The test output shows:\n```\n=== oMLX直连测试 ===\n  ok: True, dur: 6.2s\n  text: Thinking Process:...\n=== 推理路由测试（stock_screen → omlx，第1次冷调用）===\n  provider: deepseek, ok: False, dur: 0.2s\n```\n\nThe omlx call itself succeeded in 6.2s, but somehow `inference()` is reporting it as unhealthy. This suggests the health check timing is off - maybe the health check completes quickly with `ok=True`, but then something changes by the time `inference()` actually runs the omlx provider. I'm realizing the issue might be with how `_run_health_checks` updates the shared state - it acquires the lock, updates `_health_status`, but maybe the lock isn't being held long enough or there's a race condition when `is_healthy` checks the status afterward.\n\nActually, let me just bypass this deadlock-prone pattern and call `_run_health_checks` directly in `inference` without going through `is_healthy`, since I know it works when called directly. This thread-safety mess is too fragile to debug in the dark.","thinkingSignature":"0a08a98415eb57ea8b7710c38f439f23ace28dd1a7d9ecdadb87c3139a46de05"},{"type":"text","text":"The health check has a race condition. Let me simplify it - call `run_health_checks()` fresh each time in the inference router to avoid stale cache issues:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9p29y6unx9oz_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/AI-RXC/services/inference_router.py","edits":[{"oldText":"    # 检查健康状态，不健康的 provider 自动降级\n    if provider in [\"gotdx\", \"omlx\"]:\n        status = get_health_status(provider)\n        if status is False or (isinstance(status, dict) and not any(status.values())):\n            fallback = config.get(provider, {}).get(f\"fallback_{provider}_provider\") or config.get(\"default_provider\", \"deepseek\")\n            print(f\"[inference_router] {provider} 不健康，自动降级到 {fallback}\")\n            provider = fallback","newText":"    # 检查健康状态，不健康的 provider 自动降级（每次实时检查，避免缓存不一致）\n    if provider in [\"gotdx\", \"omlx\"]:\n        fresh_health = check_provider_health(provider, config)\n        if not fresh_health:\n            fallback = config.get(provider, {}).get(f\"fallback_{provider}_provider\") or config.get(\"default_provider\", \"deepseek\")\n            print(f\"[inference_router] {provider} 不健康({fresh_health})，自动降级到 {fallback}\")\n            provider = fallback"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90732,"output":1379,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127317,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776050139498,"responseId":"062b92dc1c48481262277d85f2dfead9"}}
