{"type":"message","id":"72cdbf3e","parentId":"fffa15fa","timestamp":"2026-04-13T03:24:42.291Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file doesn't exist, I need to create it and store the memories from this session.\n\nLet me summarize the important things that happened today:\n\n1. Installed gotdx (Go TDX protocol client) on Mac mini\n   - Fixed a bug in gotdx's `query.go` where `map[string]string` params failed with numeric values (Go unmarshal issue)\n   - Fixed: Changed to `map[string]interface{}`, added conversion inside `executeQuery`\n   - Installed to ~/bin/webviewer\n\n2. AI-RXC data source integration:\n   - gotdx connected to AI-RXC (via host.docker.internal:8089)\n   - gotdx K-line API bug fixed and rebuilt\n   - Real-time quotes work, K-line data now works too\n   \n3. Deployed three new components: inference caching with disk persistence, an oMLX provider for local GPU inference on Apple Silicon, and an inference router that handles task routing across different providers based on inference_routing.json configuration.\n\n4. Also created a routing configuration file and set up a gotdx health check mechanism.\n\n5. Working on the health check logic in data_source_manager.py - the `is_healthy` method calls `get_health_status` which needs to be properly connected to the health monitoring system.\n\nThe gotdx K-line bug was fixed by converting the parameter map from `map[string]string` to `map[string]interface{}` in query.go, then adding type conversion logic inside `executeQuery` to handle the interface{} values properly.\n\n6. oMLX is running on the host at port 8000 with the OmniCoder-9B-Instruct-4bit model and API key 0923, while AI-RXC runs in Docker and needs to reach it through host.docker.internal:8000.","thinkingSignature":"dffed13b9ac2437dde411c020ac3905b971395e7267d558385a323962860854a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5cl9ep9f6lze_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent/memory/2026-04-13.md","content":"# 2026-04-13 工作日志\n\n## gotdx 部署与 bug 修复\n\n- gotdx（Go TDX 协议客户端）已安装到 `~/bin/webviewer`，运行在 8089 端口\n- **重要 bug 修复**：gotdx 源码 `query.go` 中 `queryRequest.Params` 定义为 `map[string]string`，但传数字时 Go unmarshal 失败\n  - 修复：`Params` 改为 `map[string]interface{}`，`executeQuery` 内做类型转换\n  - 重编译并重启服务\n- gotdx K线 API（`/api/query` → `stock_kline`）现已正常工作\n\n## AI-RXC 数据源整合\n\n- gotdx WebViewer（8089）已通过 `host.docker.internal:8089` 接入 AI-RXC Docker\n- `get_stock_hist_data` 已优先走 gotdx（日K/周K/月K，支持前复权）\n- gotdx 修复后测试：`600519` 贵州茅台 K线 ✅\n- `data_source_manager.py` 中 `get_realtime_quotes` 有语法错误（缺少 `df =`），待修\n\n## 新增模块（豆包建议）\n\n### 1. 推理缓存层\n- 文件：`AI-RXC/services/inference_cache.py`\n- 内存 + 磁盘双层缓存，TTL 可配置（默认1小时）\n- 缓存 key：股票代码+日期+分析类型+prompt哈希\n\n### 2. oMLX Provider\n- 文件：`AI-RXC/services/llm_providers/omlx_provider.py`\n- OpenAI-compatible 接口，支持 `repetition_penalty`、`top_p` 等参数\n- oMLX server 地址：`http://host.docker.internal:8000`（从容器内访问主机）\n\n### 3. 推理路由层\n- 文件：`AI-RXC/services/inference_router.py`\n- 入口函数：`inference(task_type=, stock_code=, date=, prompt=, messages=)`\n- 配置文件：`AI-RXC/inference_routing.json`\n- 路由规则：\n  - `stock_screen` / `indicator_calc` / `pattern_match` → oMLX 本地\n  - `fund_flow_analysis` / `multi_factor` / `report_write` / `reasoning` → DeepSeek 云端\n  - oMLX 不健康时自动降级 DeepSeek\n\n### 4. 推理路由配置\n- 文件：`AI-RXC/inference_routing.json`\n- 健康检查：gotdx（60秒间隔）、omlx\n- oMLX fallback：`deepseek-chat`\n\n### 5. gotdx 健康检查\n- `DataSourceManager.is_healthy(\"gotdx\")` 方法存在，但 `get_health_status` 方法未实现（方法体 pass）\n- `get_realtime_quotes` 中有语法错误：`if self.gotdx_client and self.is_healthy(\"gotdx\"):` 后面缺少 `df =`\n\n## 当前系统状态\n\n| 服务 | 地址 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| AI-RXC (Docker) | localhost:8503 | ✅ 运行中 |\n| gotdx WebViewer | 127.0.0.1:8089 | ✅ 运行中 |\n| oMLX server | 127.0.0.1:8000 | ✅ 运行中 |\n| OpenClaw | 主机 | ✅ 运行中 |\n\n## 待完成事项\n\n1. 修复 `data_source_manager.py` 中 `get_realtime_quotes` 的语法错误\n2. `DataSourceManager.get_health_status()` 方法实现为空，需补充\n3. oMLX 本地推理实际效果待验证（OmniCoder-9B-Instruct-4bit 在 Mac Mini M4 上）\n4. 健康检查 OpenClaw cron 任务待设置（定时 ping gotdx/omlx）\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32871,"output":1232,"cacheRead":12322,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46425,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776050644441,"responseId":"062b94d501eb0b6d862b4d67a10a9491"}}
