{"type":"message","id":"735c5448","parentId":"73012683","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:38:46.681Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"While waiting for the build, let me also check the gotdx health check issue more carefully. The health check in `inference_router.py` was using `httpx.get` instead of `httpx.post`. I've fixed that. Let me also think about what other \"blocking items\" there might be.\n\nThe user said \"解决所有堵塞项\" (resolve all blocking items). This is quite vague. Let me think about what could be blocking:\n\n1. Docker commands hanging - resolved by using `DOCKER_HOST` explicitly\n2. gotdx health check returning false even when service is working - just fixed with POST change\n\n\n3. The `inference_router.py` needs to pass `timeout` properly to `httpx.post`, and I should verify that the gotdx health check also needs that same fix.","thinkingSignature":"627014c44b841a668f5ee55fb92957590b361c6cdcd9a7027946e107fb11d9b5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pxkvvuqk6e60_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/AI-RXC/services/inference_router.py","offset":22,"limit":40}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94764,"output":223,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130193,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776065918877,"responseId":"062bd07fbaf319374b0ccd216fc63319"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4f45474","parentId":"735c5448","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:38:46.796Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pxkvvuqk6e60_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"_health_lock = Lock()\n\n\ndef _load_routing_config() -> dict:\n    path = os.environ.get(\"INFERENCE_ROUTING_CONFIG\", _ROUTING_CONFIG_PATH)\n    if os.path.exists(path):\n        with open(path) as f:\n            return json.load(f)\n    return {}\n\n\ndef check_provider_health(provider: str, config: dict) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"检查 provider 是否健康\"\"\"\n    try:\n        if provider == \"gotdx\":\n            import httpx\n            base_url = config.get(\"gotdx\", {}).get(\"base_url\", \"http://host.docker.internal:8089\")\n            method = config.get(\"gotdx\", {}).get(\"health_check_method\", \"stock_quotes\")\n            resp = httpx.post(f\"{base_url}/api/query\", timeout=3, json={\n                \"method\": method,\n                \"params\": {\"markets\": \"0,1\", \"codes\": \"000001\"}\n            })\n            return resp.status_code == 200\n        elif provider == \"omlx\":\n            import httpx\n            omlx_cfg = config.get(\"omlx\", {})\n            base_url = omlx_cfg.get(\"base_url\", \"http://host.docker.internal:8000\")\n            api_key = omlx_cfg.get(\"api_key\", \"0923\")\n            base = base_url.rstrip(\"/\")\n            if base.endswith(\"/v1\"):\n                base = base[:-3]\n            resp = httpx.get(\n                f\"{base}/v1/models\",\n                timeout=5,\n                headers={\"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {api_key}\"}\n            )\n            return resp.status_code == 200\n    except Exception:\n        pass\n    return False\n\n[124 more lines in file. Use offset=62 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776065926778}}
