{"type":"message","id":"fc5cdf36","parentId":"c8e002f6","timestamp":"2026-04-13T07:40:17.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear now - the gotdx health check uses `{\"markets\": \"0,1\", \"codes\": \"000001\"}` but the API says \"markets 数量必须和代码数量一致\" (the number of markets must match the number of codes). \n\nSince we have 2 market codes (\"0,1\"), we need 2 stock codes. Or we should use `markets: 0` and `codes: \"000001\"`.\n\nLet me fix the health check in `inference_router.py`.","thinkingSignature":"3bc95f363fe2b84e94a976171d00e67a45aec5a1d2320b8cb2475abfb3b8eda8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dud7vx7sd0wj_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/AI-RXC/services/inference_router.py","edits":[{"oldText":"            resp = httpx.post(f\"{base_url}/api/query\", timeout=3, json={\n                \"method\": method,\n                \"params\": {\"markets\": \"0,1\", \"codes\": \"000001\"}\n            })\n            return resp.status_code == 200","newText":"            resp = httpx.post(f\"{base_url}/api/query\", timeout=3, json={\n                \"method\": method,\n                \"params\": {\"markets\": 0, \"codes\": \"000001\"}\n            })\n            return resp.status_code == 200"}]}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":96966,"output":291,"cacheRead":35206,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132463,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776066007366,"responseId":"062bd0d701513856df03b53a35ade0c8"}}
