{"type":"message","id":"4353de7b","parentId":"d6c7cc79","timestamp":"2026-04-13T09:25:36.018Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! 20260413 (today) has 5494 rows, and 20260410 has 5495 rows. So Tushare has data for these dates already. The `daily_basic_all_2019_2026.csv` file just needs to be updated with these new rows.\n\nThe `download_tushare.py` script doesn't update daily_basic. Let me look at whether I can just append the new daily_basic data to the CSV.Actually, let me just check if I can run the `run_paper_trading_profiles_v1.sh` script but with the FORCE_REFRESH=0 and after manually updating the daily_basic CSV file. \n\nRather than trying to patch the existing download script, I should focus on what the paper profiles actually need. They require positions, account data, and orders—these are generated by the trading simulation itself. The staleness issue stems from the signal chain failing due to stale daily_basic. So my best bet is to refresh the daily_basic CSV with the new data, then re-run the paper profile generation without the FORCE_REFRESH flag to avoid regenerating the signals.","thinkingSignature":"0685e31b26fdafbe145ec4e73da31d00537fbe002e42fcffc9dd5046ac2e2564"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1e1jm9kt9k8u_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport tushare as ts\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\npro = ts.pro_api('e3d8c68a414b9a84cbc49c637ec00875c7173a961eba98cff09c1afc')\n\n# 获取每日指标数据（更新到最新）\nbasic_path = '/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/daily_basic_all_2019_2026.csv'\nexisting = pd.read_csv(basic_path)\nprint(f'现有: {len(existing)} 行, 最新日期: {existing[\\\"trade_date\\\"].max()}')\n\n# 增量获取最近5个交易日的数据\nfor d in ['20260410', '20260411', '20260413']:\n    try:\n        df = pro.daily_basic(ts_code='', trade_date=d)\n        if len(df) > 0:\n            df['trade_date'] = d\n            existing2 = pd.read_csv(basic_path)\n            new_rows = df[~df['trade_date'].astype(str).isin(existing2['trade_date'].astype(str))]\n            if len(new_rows) > 0:\n                combined = pd.concat([existing2, new_rows], ignore_index=True)\n                combined.to_csv(basic_path, index=False)\n                print(f'已追加 {d}: {len(new_rows)} 行')\n            else:\n                print(f'{d}: 无需更新')\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f'{d}: err={e}')\n\" 2>&1","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":61424,"output":593,"cacheRead":35406,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97423,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776072320094,"responseId":"062be980ae2b73eeb4f63de6a4b9980e"}}
