{"type":"message","id":"1f9bb3fd","parentId":"cd25f474","timestamp":"2026-04-13T13:13:09.825Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The skill is installed. Let me now check if there are npm dependencies that need to be installed for this skill, and if there's a config template.","thinkingSignature":"b0cae06c9552c3ff8e7c63f9610e553d4b85bf8f002a94d6a85feee4306024c8"},{"type":"text","text":"安装成功！✅\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/skills/auto-backup-openclaw-user-data/\n├── SKILL.md\n├── README.md\n├── scripts/\n│   ├── backup.js      # 主备份逻辑\n│   ├── config.js      # 配置管理\n│   ├── compressor.js  # ZIP 压缩\n│   ├── scheduler.js   # 定时任务\n│   ├── cleaner.js     # 清理旧备份\n│   └── notifier.js    # 消息通知\n├── templates/\n│   └── config.template.json\n└── HEARTBEAT_prompt_example.md\n```\n\n**功能：**\n- 定时自动备份 `.openclaw` 目录\n- ZIP 压缩 + 保留策略\n- 支持 Cron / HEARTBEAT 两种调度方式\n- 多渠道通知（飞书等）\n\n需要初始化配置才能启用定时备份。要现在配置吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95966,"output":214,"cacheRead":35406,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131586,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776085981960,"responseId":"062c1ede010cca3d8ec15252272b78ea"}}
